hadiths[282]{hadithnumber,text}:
2223,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ki (apni ummat ke barey mein) eik dua qubul hoti hai, isliye her Nabi ne dua karney mein jaldi ki, jabkey maine apni dua ko apni ummat ki shafaat ke liye roze-qiyamat ke liye chupa rakha hai, aur wo (shafa'at) Insha-Allah her us shakhs ko pahunchey gi jo is haal mein faut hua hoga ke usney Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraya hoga.'' Muslim. aur Bukhari ki riwayat is se mukhtasar hai. muttafaq aleh, rawahu Muslim aur Al Bukhari (6304)."
2224,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! maine tujh se eik ehad liya hai be-shak jiske to khilaf nahin kerega, main bhi eik insan hun, maine jis kisi momin ko aziyat pahunchaai ho, maine usey bura bhala kaha ho, laanat malamat ki ho, usey maara ho to us (aziyat) ko uskey liye baaise rehmat aur tahaarat aur baaise qurbat bana dey aur roze-qiyamat us qurbat ki wajeh se to usey apna muqarrab bana ley.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari (6341) aur Muslim."
2225,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi dua karey to yun na kahe : aey Allah ! agar to chahey to mujhey bakhsh dey , agar to chahey to mujh par rehem farma , agar to chahey to mujhey rizq ata farma, balke usey chahiye ke wo purey azm ke sath dua karey, kyonkey wo jaisey chahey karta hai, usey koi majbur karney wala nahin.'' (Bukhari 7477)."
2226,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi dua karey to yun na kahe : aey Allah ! agar to chahey to mujhey bakhsh dey , balke usey pukhta azm ke sath aur badi raghbat (dichaspi) ke sath dua karni chahiye, kyonkey kisi bhi chiz ka ata karna Allah ke liye koi giraan (mushkil) nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
2227,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda jab tak kisi gunah ya qata' rehmi ke barey mein dua na karey uski dua qubul hoti hai. ba-sharte-ke wo jald bazi na karey.'' arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! jald bazi se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kehta hai : main to bahut duaen kar chuka lekin meri dua qubul hi nahin hoti , us soorate-haal mein wo mayus ho jata hai aur dua karna chhod deta hai.'' rawahu Muslim aur Bukhari (6340)."
2228,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman shakhs ki apney (musalman) bhai ke liye wo dua qubul hoti hai jo uski ghair mojudgi mein ki jati hai, aur (dua karney waley) ke paas eik farishta maamoor hota hai, jab wo apney bhai ke liye duaaey khair karta hai to wo maamoor farishta Aameen kehta hai aur kehta hai : isi ke jaisi tumharey liye bhi ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
2229,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni aulad aur apney amwaal ke liye badduaa na karo, kahin aisa na ho ke tum kisi aisi ghadi mein Allah se dua kar betho jis mein dua qubul ho jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim. aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''mazloom ki badduaa se bacho ''kitabuz-zakat mein zikr ki gaee hai."
2230,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua hi ibadat hai, phir aapney ye aayat padhi : ''tumharey rab ne farmaya : mujh se duaeyn karo main tumhari duaeyn qubul karunga.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 267 padhi. 18542 , 276 padhi. 18623 ), Tirmizi ( 2969 ), Abu-Dawood ( 1479 ), Nasai (الکبری : 11464 ), ibne-Maja ( 3828 ),  ibne-Hibban ( 2394 (aur al-Hakim (1 / 490 , 491 ( ."
2231,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua ibadat ka maghz hai.'' (zaeef sanad) rawahu Tirmizi ( 3371 )."
2232,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke yahan dua se behtar koi chiz nahin .'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3370 (aur ibne-Maja ( 3829 )."
2233,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf dua hi qaza ko taal sakti hai. aur sirf neki aur itaat hi umr daraz kar sakti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2139 (aur ibne-Maja ( 90 , 4022 ( ."
2234,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua un masaayib (musibaton) ke liye nafa-mand hai jo nazil ho chukey aur unke liye bhi jo abhi nazil nahin huye, Allah ke bando ! duayen kiya karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3515 , 3548 (aur ibne-Maja ( 3551 ( ."
2235,"Aur Imam Ahmed ne Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 234  22394) ."
2236,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi shakhs dua karta hai. jis mein gunah ya qata' rehmi na ho, to Allah Taala us shakhs ko uski matlooba chiz hi ata farma deta hai ya phir uski jaisi takleef us se door kar deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi (3381, 3573)."
2237,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se uska Fazal talab kiya karo kyonkey Allah pasand karta hai ke us se sawal kiya jaey aur kashaaish w khushhali ka intizar afzal ibadat hai.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3571 )."
2238,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah se sawal nahin karta to wo is par naraz hota hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi (3373) aur ibne-Maja (3827)."
2239,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jis shakhs ke liye dua ka darwaza khol diya gaya to uskey liye rehmat ke darwazey khol diye gaey, aur Allah ko ye bahut pasand hai ke us se aafiyat ka sawal kiya jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3548 )."
2240,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko pasand ho ke mushkilat aur musibaton ke waqt Allah Taala uski dua qubul farmaai to phir usey chahiye ke wo khushhali mein kasrat se duayen karey.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi (3382).
2241,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua ki qubuliyat ke yaqin ke sath Allah se dua karo, aur jaan lo Allah qalbe-ghafil se ki gaee dua qubul nahin farmata .'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3479 (aur Ahmed (2 / 177)."
2242,"Hazrat Malik bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Allah se dua karo to us se sidhey haathon se dua karo aur us se ultey haathon se dua na karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 1486 ( ."
2243,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''Allah se sidhey haathon se dua kiya karo, ultey haathon se dua na kiya karo, aur jab tum (dua sey) farigh ho jaao to un (haathon) ko apney chehron par pher liya karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood (1485)."
2244,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara rab bada hayaadaar , sakhi daata hai, jab banda uskey samney haath failata hai to usey khaali lautaate huey usey haya aati hai.'' ,( rawahu Tirmizi ( 3556 ), Abu-Dawood ( 1477 )  al-Behaqi fi  (1 / 137 padhi. 180 , 181 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3865 ( ."
2245,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua ke liye haath uthaya kartey they to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen chehrey par pher kar nichey giraya kartey they. (rawahu Tirmizi ( 3385 (aur al-Adab  ( 609 )."
2246,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jaame duayen karna pasand kartey they aur unke ilawa baqi duayen chhod diya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 1482 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban ( 2412 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 539 ( ."
2247,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi shakhs ke liye ghair-mojudgi mein ki gaee dua bahut jald qubul hoti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 1980 (aur Abu-Dawood (1535)."
2248,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Umre ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey ijazat ata ki aur farmaya : ''piyaarey bhai ! hamen apni dua mein yad rakhna aur hamein bhool na jana.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisi baat farmaee jiskey badley mein puri duniya ka husool merey liye baaise musarrat nahin. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi . aur Imam Tirmizi ki riwayat (ولا تنسنا) ke alfaz par khatam ho jati hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood (1497) aur Tirmizi (3562)."
2249,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen aadmiyon ki dua zarur qubul hoti hai, roza daar jab wo iftaar ke waqt dua karta hai, aadil badshah aur duaaey mazloom , Allah is (dua) ko badalon ke ooper utha leta hai, uskey liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur rab farmata hai : meri izzat ki qism ! main zarur tumhari madad karunga chahey (chaahe) kuchh der se ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi (3598), ibne-Maja ( 1753 ), sahi ibne Khuzaima ( 1901 (aur ibne-Hibban (2407 , 2408)."
2250,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen duayen aisi hain jin ki qubuliyat mein koi shak nahin, walid ki dua, musafir ki dua aur mazloom ki dua.'' rawahu Tirmizi (1905), Abu-Dawood (1536), ibne-Maja ( 3862 (aur sahi ibne-Hibban (2406)."
2251,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se her shakhs ko apni tamam zarooratein apney rab se maangni chahiyen yahan tak ke jab uskey jootey ka tasma toot jaey to uskey barey mein bhi usi se sawal karna chahiye.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 8 / 406 )."
2252,Aur Sabit Bunaani se marwi (bayan) mursal riwayat mein itna izafa hai : ''yahan tak ke wo namak bhi us se maangey aur yahan tak ke jab uska tasma toot jaey to wo bhi us se maangey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 9 / 3604 ( .
2253,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dorane-dua apney haath is qadr buland farmatey ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aaney lagti.  (rawahu al-Behaqi fi (1 / 138 padhi. 182) , Muslim w Ahmed ( 3 / 259 ( ."
2254,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni haathon ki ungliyan kandhon ke barabar kiya kartey they aur dua farmatey they. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi  (1 / 140 185 ( , al-Hakim (1 / 535 , 536 padhi. 1964 (aur Abu-Dawood (1105)."
2255,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they to aap haath uthatey aur phir apney haath chehrey par pher letey they. Imam Behaqi ne teeno ahadis ( الدعوات الکبیر ) mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi (1 / 139 , 140 padhi. 181 ), Abu-Dawood ( 1492 )."
2256,"Hazrat Ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain, dua (ka adab) ye hai ke tum apney haath kandhon ya taqriban kandhon ke barabar uthao, talab maghfirat (ka adab ( ye hai ke tum eik ungli (angusht shahadat) ke sath ishara karo aur narmi, aajizi ye hai tum apney dono haath daraz kar do. aur eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : narmi w aajizi is tarah hai aur unhoney apney haath is qadr buland kiye aur haathon ki pusht ko apney chehrey ki taraf kiya. rawahu Abu-Dawood (1489, 1490)."
2257,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo farmaya kartey they : tumhara (dua ke liye) haath uthana bidat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us (yani) seeney se ooper haath nahin uthatey they. rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 61,  5264 ( ."
2258,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ko yad farmatey to uskey liye dua farmatey aur pehley apney liye kartey. Tirmizi . aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3385 (aur Abu-Dawood ( 3984 ).
2259,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman koi aisi dua karta hai jis mein gunah aur qata' rehmi na ho to Allah us wajeh se teen chizon mein se koi eik usey ata farma deta hai : ya to uski dua fauran qubul farma leta hai ya usey uskey liye aakhirat mein zakhira kar leta hai ya phir uski jaisi takleef us se door farma deta hai. Sahaba ne arz kiya, tab to ham ziyada duayen karengey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah (duaeyn qubul karney mein) bahut ziyada hai.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed ( 3 / 17,  11150 ), abd bin Humaid ( 937 ), Bukhari  ( 710 ( aural-Haakim (1 / 463 )."
2260,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch duaeyn hain jo qubul ki jati hain : mazloom ki dua yahan tak ke wo intiqam le-ley , haaji ki dua yahan tak ke wo wapis aa jaey, Mujahid ki dua yahan tak ke wo ( jihad sey) farigh ho jaey. mareez ki dua yahan tak ke wo sehat yaab ho jaey aur bhai ki dua jo wo apney ( musalman ( bhai ke liye uski ghair-mojudgi mein karta hai.'' phir farmaya : ''in duaaon mein bhai ki ghaaibaana dua bahut jald qubul hoti hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi,  rawahu fi-Shobil-Emaan : 1125 , nuskha muhaqqiqa : 1087)."
2261,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kuchh log beth kar Allah ka zikr kartey hain to farishtey unhen gher letey hain, rehmat unhen dhanp leti hai, un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai aur Allah apney yahan farishton ke paas uska tazkira farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka ki Shah raah par safar mein they, aap Jumdaan naami pahad ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''chaltey jaao ye jamdaan hai.'' phir farmaya : ''Mufridun sabqat ley gaey.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mufridun kon log hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka kasrat se zikr karney waley mard aur aurten.'' rawahu Muslim."
2263,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shakhs jo apney rab ka zikr karta hai wo zinde ki tarah hai aur wo shakhs jo zikr nahin karta murde ki tarah hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6407 aur Muslim"
2264,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main apney bandey ke guman ke sath hun, jab wo mujhey yad karta hai to main uskey sath hota hun, agar wo mujhey apney dil mein yad karta hai to main bhi usey apney dil mein yad karta hun aur agar wo mujhey kisi jamaat mein yad karta hai to main usey us se behtar ( farishton ki) jamaat mein yad karta hun.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7405 aur Muslim."
2265,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : jo shakhs eik neki lekar aaeyga to uskey liye das guna sawab hai aur main usey badha dunga, aur jo shakhs burai lekar aaeyga to burai ka badla uske jaise hi hoga ya phir main bakhsh dunga, jo shakhs baalisht barabar merey qarib aata hai to main eik haath ( taqriban eik meetar ( uskey qarib ho jata hun, aur jo shakhs eik haath merey qarib hota hai to main do haath uskey qarib ho jata hun, jo shakhs chalta hua merey paas aata hai to main daudta hua uskey paas aata hun. jo shakhs zamin bhar kar gunah lekar merey paas aaeyga to main usi qadr maghfirat lekar us se mulaqat karunga ba-sharte-ke wo merey sath kisi ko shareek na thehrata ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
2266,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs merey kisi pasandida shakhs se dushmani rakhey to mera us se aelane-jang hai, aur mera banda jin-jin ibadat ke zariey mera qurb hasil karta hai un mein se wo ibadat mujhey bahut mehbub hai jo maine is par farz ki hai. mera banda nawaafil ke zariey mera qurb hasil karta rehta hai yahan tak ke main us se mohabbat karney lagta hun, jab main us se mohabbat karta hun to main uska kaan bin jata hun jis se wo sunta hai, uski aankh bin jata hun jis se wo dekhta hai, uska haath bin jata hun jis se wo pakadta hai, uska paaon bin jata hun jis se wo chalta hai, aur agar wo mujh se koi chiz maangta hai to main usey ata kar deta hun, agar wo mujh se panah talab karta hai to main usey panah dey deta hun, maine jo kaam karna hota hai uskey karney mein mujhey kabhi itna taraddud (sankoch) nahin hota jitna kisi momin ki jaan qabz kartey waqt taraddud hota hai wo maut ko nagawar janta hai aur main uski eza (takleef) ko nagawar janta hun, halanke wo (maut) to usey zarur aani hai.'' Bukhari (6508)."
2267,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke kuchh farishtey hain jo ehale zikar ko talash kartey huey raaston mein chakkar lagatey rehtey hain, jab wo kuch logon ko Allah ka zikr kartey huey pa letey hain to wo eik doosrey ko aawaz detey hain, apney maqsad (ehale zikr) ki taraf aao.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo apney paron ke zariey unhen gher letey hain aur aasmane-duniya tak pahunch jatey hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unka rab un se poochhtey hai, halanke wo unhen behtar janta hai, merey bandey kya kehtey hain ?'' farmaya : '' wo arz kartey hain : wo teri tasbih aur takbir aur teri hamd aur sanaa bayan kartey hain.'' farmaya : ''wo farmata hai : kya unhoney mujhey dekha hai? wo arz kartey hain : nahin, Allah ki qism ! unhoney tujhey nahin dekha.'' farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : agar wo mujhey dekh lein to phir unki kaifiyat kaisi ho?'' farmaya : ''wo arz kartey hain, agar wo tujhey dekh lein to wo teri khub ibadat karen, khub shaan aur azmat bayan karen aur teri bahut ziyada tasbih bayan keren.'' farmaya , wo poochhtey hai : ''wo (mujh sey) kya mang rahey hain? wo arz kartey hain, wo tujh se jannat mang rahey hain.'' farmaya : ''wo poochhtey hai, kya unhoney usey dekha hai? to wo arz kartey hain : nahin, Allah ki qism ! aey rab ! unhoney usey nahin dekha .''  farmaya : '' wo poochhtey hai : agar wo usey dekh lein to phir kaisi kaifiyat ho?'' farmaya : ''wo arz kartey hain, agar wo usey dekh lein to wo uski bahut ziyada khahish , chaahat aur raghbat rakhen.'' farmaya : ''Allah taala poochhtey hai : wo kis chiz se panah talab kartey hain?'' farmaya : ''wo arz kartey hain : jahannam se.'' farmaya : ''wo poochhtey hai : kya unhoney usey dekha hai?''  farmaya : ''wo arz kartey hain : nahin, Allah ki qism ! aey rab ! unhoney usey nahin dekha.'' farmaya : ''wo poochhtey hai : agar wo usey dekh lein to phir kaisi kaifiyat ho?'' farmaya : ''wo arz kartey hain : agar wo usey dekh lein to wo us se bahut door bhagen aur us se bahut ziyada darengey.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine unhen bakhsh diya hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik farishta arz karta hai : un mein falan shakhs aisa hai jo ke un (yani ehle zikr ( mein se nahin, wo to kisi zarurat ke tehat aaya tha, farmaya : wo aisey bethney waley hain ke unka ham nasheen mehroom nahin reh sakta.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ke kuchh faazil farishtey hain jo chakkar lagatey rehtey hain aur wo zikr ki majaalis talash kartey hain, jab wo zikr ki koi majlis pa letey hain to wo bhi unke sath beth jatey hain, aur apney paron ke zariey unhen gher letey hain yahan tak ke wo un  (zaakreen) ke aur aasmane-duniya ke beech khala (khaali jagah) ko bhar detey hain, jab wo (zaakreen) majlis se uth jatey hain, to wo farishtey aasman ki taraf chadh jatey hain, farmaya : to Allah un se poochhtey hai, halanke wo (unke haalat ko) janta hai, tum kahan se aaye ho? wo arz kartey hain, ham zamin se terey un bandon ke paas se aaye hain jo teri tasbih aur takbir aur tahleel aur tahmeed bayan kartey hain aur tujh se maangtey hain, farmaya : wo mujh se kya maangtey hain? wo arz kartey hain, wo tujh se teri jannat maangtey hain, farmaya : kya unhoney meri jannat dekhi hai? wo arz kartey hain, aey rab ! nahin, farmaya : agar wo meri jannat dekh lein to phir kaisi kaifiyat ho? wo arz kartey hain, wo tujh se panah talab kartey hain, farmaya : wo mujh se kis chiz se panah talab kar rahey they? wo arz kartey hain, teri jahannam sey, farmaya : kya unhoney meri jahannam ko dekha hai? wo arz kartey hain, nahin, farmaya : agar wo meri jahannam ko dekh lein to phir kaisi kaifiyat ho? wo arz kartey hain : wo tujh se maghfirat talab kartey hain.'' farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : maine unhen bakhsh diya, unhoney jo manga maine dey diya aur unhoney jis chiz se panah talab ki, maine unhen us se panah de-di .'' farmaya : ''wo (farishtey) arz kartey hain : rab ji ! un main eik aisa gunah gaar shakhs hai ke bas wo guzar raha tha aur unke sath beth gaya.'' farmaya : ''Allah Rabbul-Izzat kehtey hain : maine usey bhi bakhsh diya, wo aisey log hain ke unka ham nashen mehroom nahin reh sakta. '' Bukhari 6408 aur Muslim."
2268,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Rabeea Usaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey miley to unhoney puchha : Hanzala ! kaisey ho? maine arz kiya : Hanzala munafiq ho gaya, unhoney farmaya : Subhanallah ! tum kya keh rahey ho? maine kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hotey hain, wo jahannam aur jannat (ki tarheeb aur targheeb) ke zariey hamein nasihat kartey rehtey hain, goya ham khud dekh rahey hain, aur jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se aa jatey hain aur azwaj (jodey) (biwi) aur aulad aur zaraey muaash mein mashghool ho jatey hain to ham bahut kuchh bhool jatey hain, is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! hamari bhi yehi sooratehaal hai. main aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) chaltey gaey yahan tak ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey, to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Hanzala munafiq ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya hua?'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap ki khidmat mein hotey hain to aap jannat aur dozakh ke zariey hamen nasihat farmatey hain goya ham usey khud aakhon se dekh rahey hain, aur jab ham aap ke paas se aa jatey hain, aur apney maal bachchon aur zaraey muaash mein mashghool ho jatey hain to ham bahut kuchh bhool jatey hain, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tumhari jo kaifiyat merey paas hoti hai aur tum zikr ki jis surat mein hotey ho, agar tumhari wo kaifiyat hamesha rahey to farishtey tumharey bistaron par aur tumharey raaston main tum se musaafa keren.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba farmaya : ''lekin Hanzala ! kisi waqt aisey aur kisi waqt aisey (hota hai).'' rawahu Muslim."
2269,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen tumharey behtareen amal ke barey mein na bataaun jo ke tumharey Malik ke yahan ajr ke lihaz se ziyada badhney wala, tumharey buland darjaat ka baais ka banney wala, tumharey liye soney , aur chaandi ke kharch karney se behtar aur tumharey liye dushman se aisa jihad karney se behtar jis main tum eik doosrey ki gardanen udaao?'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, kyon nahin ! zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka zikr.'' Maalik , Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja . albatta Imam Malik ne usey abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf qarar diya hai.  Hasan (rawahu Malik (1 / 211, 493 ), Ahmed ( 4 / 447,  28075 , 5 / 195 ), Tirmizi ( 3377 (aur ibne-Maja  (3790)."
2270,"Hazrat Abdullah bin basar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : kon se log behtar hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ke liye khushkhabri hai jiski umr daraz ho aur uska amal achchhaa ho.'' usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa amal behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''martey waqt teri zaban par Allah ka zikr jari ho.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 188 padhi. 17832 (aur Tirmizi ( 2329 , 3375 ( ."
2271,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum baaghaate-jannat ke paas se guzro to wahan se kha liya karo.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, baaghaate-jannat kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zikr ke halqey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3510 )."
2272,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi jagah bethey aur wahan Allah ka zikr na karey to is par Allah ki taraf se nuqsan hoga, aur jo shakhs kisi jagah letey aur wahan Allah ka zikr na karey to is par Allah ki taraf se nuqsan hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood (4856)."
2273,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log kisi aisi majlis se uthen jahan unhoney Allah ka zikr na kiya ho to wo aisey uthen gey jaisey kisi gadhey ki badbudar laash se uthey hon. aur ye (majlis roze-qiyamat) unke liye baaise-hasrat hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed (2 / 515, 10691) aur Abu-Dawood ( 4855 )."
2274,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log kisi majlis mein beth kar Allah ka zikr karen na apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood bhejein to ye ( majlis ( unke liye baaise hasrat aur nuqsan hogi , agar wo chahey to unhen azab dey aur agar chaahey to unhen bakhsh dey.'' (rawahu Tirmizi ( 3380 ), Ahmed ( 2 / 463,  9965 aur sanad sahih)"
2275,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''amr-bil-maaroof ya nahi anin-munkar ya Allah ke zikr ke siwa, ibne-Adam ka tamam kalam is par bojh hai, wo uskey liye nafamand nahin.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2412 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3974 ( ."
2276,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke zikr ke siwa ziyada baaten na kya karo, kyonkey Allah ke zikr ke siwa ziyada baaten karna dil ki sakhti ki wajah hain. aur sakht dil shakhs Allah se koson door hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2411 ("
2277,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat ( وَالَّذِیْنَ یَکْنِزُوْنَ الذَّھَبَ وَالْفِضَّۃَ ( nazil hui to ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kisi safar mein shareek they, to aap ke baaz Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : soney aur chaandi ke barey main to aayat nazil ho gaee , kaash! ! ham jaan lein ke kon sa maal behtar hai taake ham usey hasil kar lein ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab se afzal maal zikr karney wali zaban, shukr karney wala dil aur momina shareeke-hayaat jo uskey eman ke barey mein uski muaawinat karey. rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 278 padhi. 22751 ( w Tirmizi (3096) w ibne-Maja ( 1856 ( ."
2278,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) masjid ke eik halqey ke paas aaye to farmaya : tum kyon bethey ho? unhoney kaha : ham Allah ka zikr karney ke liye bethey hain, unhoney farmaya : kya tum Allah ki qism uthatey ho ke tum sirf usi liye bethey ho? unhoney kaha : ham Allah ki qism uthatey hain ke ham sirf usi liye bethey hain. unhoney farmaya : maine tumharey mutalliq kis bad-gumaani ki wajeh se tum se qism nahin uthwaai, aur aap mein se koi aisa nahin jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mujh jaisi qurbat ho iskey bawajud maine kam hadisein bayan ki hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ke eik halqey mein tashrif laye to un se farmaya : ''tum yahan kyon bethey ho? unhoney arz kya : ham Allah ka zikr karney aur is baat par uska shukr ada karney ke liye bethey hain ke usney Islam ki taraf hamari raahnumai farmaai aur uskey zariey ham par ehsan kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum Allah ki qism uthatey ho ke tum sirf isi liye bethey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ki qism ! ham sirf isi liye bethey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumharey mutalliq kisi bad-gumaani ki wajeh se tum se qism nahin uthwaai, balke Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas tashrif laye to unhoney mujhey bataya ke Allah azz-w-jall tumhari wajeh se farishton par fakhr farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2279,"Hazrat Abdullah bin basar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne arz kya Allah ke Rasool ! sharaaia Islam (farz, nafli ibadat) mujh par ghalib aa gaey, aap kisi eik chiz ke mutalliq mujhey bataeyn ke main uskey sath tamassuk ( lagaao ( ikhtiyar kar lun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teri zaban par her waqt Allah ka zikr jari rehna chahiye.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3375 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3793 ( ."
2280,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya roze-qiyamat kon log Allah ke yahan fazilat w rifat ke aalaa darjey par faaiz hongey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kasrat se Allah ka zikr karney waley mard aur kasrat se zikr karney wali aurten.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool! Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley se bhi afzal? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar-che wo kuffar w mushrekin se is qadr talwaar ke sath ladaai karey ke wo talwaar toot jaey aur wo khoon se rangin ho jaey tab bhi Allah ka zikr karney wala us se darje mein afzal hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed ( 3 / 75  11743 ( w Tirmizi ( 3376 ( ."
2281,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shetan ibne-Adam ke dil ke sath chimta rehta hai, jab wo Allah ka zikr karta hai to wo peechey hat jata hai, aur jab wo ghafil hota hai to wo waswasey daalta hai.'' Imam Bukhari ne usey muallaq riwayat kya hai. ( Bukhari (4977 tafseer Sura Naas ( w rawahu ibn Jarir Tabri al-Hakim"
2282,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey khabar pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' ghaflat ke shikar logon mein Allah ka zikr karney wala maidane-jihad se raah farar ikhtiyar karney walon ke baad qitaal karney waley ki tarah hai, aur ghafil logon mein Allah ka zikr karney wala khushk darkht mein sabz (hara) shaakh ki tarah hai.'' ( rawahu Malik)"
2283,"aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' (us ki misal aisey hai) jaisey khushk darakhton main eik sarsabz darkht ho. aur ghafilon mein Allah ka zikr karney wala taareek kamrey mein chiragh ki tarah hai. ghafilon mein Allah ka zikr karney waley ko Allah uski zindagi mein uska jannat mein maqam dikha deta hai, aur Allah , ghafilon mein uska zikr karney waley ke behtreen kalaam w Aajam ki tadaad ke barabar gunah bakhsh deta hai.'' behtreen kalam se insan aur Aajam se haiwaan murad hain. rawahu rizeen ( انظر الحدیث السابق : 2282 ( ."
2284,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Adam ke tamam aamaal mein sey, azabe-ilaahi se usey sab se ziyada najat dilaney wala amal, Allah ka zikr hai.'' rawahu Malik (1 / 211 padhi. 493 ( w Tirmizi ( 337 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3790 ("
2285,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main apney bandey ke sath hota hun, jab wo mera zikr karta hai aur merey ( zikr ke) sath uskey hont harkat kartey hain.'' (Bukhari Tauheed baab 43) w Ahmed ( 2 / 540 ( w ibne-Maja ( 2792 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 2316 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 496 ( ."
2286,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''her chiz ke liye eik safai karney wali chiz hoti hai, jabkey dilon ki safai karney wali chiz Allah ka zikr hai, aur Allah ke zikr se badh kar, Allah ke azab se bachaney wali koi chiz nahin .'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ki raah mein jihad karna bhi nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, agar-che wo apni talwaar is qadr chalaey ke wo toot jaey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi w Shobil-emaan ( 522 , 519 ( ."
2287,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ke ninnanwey, eik kam so naam hain, jo unhen yad kar ley wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' wo witr (yakta) hai aur witr ko pasand karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6410 , 7392 w Muslim"
2288,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ke ninnanwey eik kam so naam hain, jo unhen yad kar ley wo jannat mein dakhil hoga : wo Allah hai jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo bahut meharban , nihayat rehem karney wala hai, wo badshah hai, wo paak w munazzah, salamti deney wala, aman deney wala, nigehban , ghalib , jabbaar w mutakabbir , paida karney wala, adam se wajood mein laney wala, tasweer kashi karney wala, bakhshney wala, tamam makhluq par ghalib , ata karney wala, rizq deney wala, faisla karney wala, janney wala, tangi door karney wala, faraakhi karney wala, ooper karney wala, izzat deney wala, zillat deney wala, dekhney wala, hukm deney wala, adl karney wala, bareek dekhnewala, khabar rakhney wala, azmat wala, bakhshney wala, qadr daan , buland , bada , hifazat karney wala, nigrani karney wala, kifaayat karney wala '' shaan w buzurgi wala, sakhi data , hifazat karney wala, duayen qubul karney wala, kashaaish wala, hikmat wala, mohabbat rakhney wala, shaan w shokat wala, mardon ko dobara zindagi ata karney wala, hazir , Sabit , karsaz , qawi , taqat wala, madadgar , qabile-sataaish , ehata karney wala, pehli baar paida karney wala, dobara paida karney wala, maarney wala, zindagi bakhshney wala, qaaim rehney aur qaaim rakhney wala, paalney wala, buzurgi wala, yakta , tanha, be niaz , qadir w muqtadir , aagey karney wala, peechey karney wala, awwal , aakhir , zahir , baatin , tamam ashiya ka Malik , buland tar , ehsan karney wala, tauba qubul karney wala, intiqam leney wala, darguzar karney wala, shafqat karney wala, shahanshaah , azmat w ikram wala, roze-qiyamat jama karney wala, ghani be-niaz karney wala, rokney wala, nuqsan pahunchaney wala, nafa deney wala, mujassam Noor, raah dikhaney wala, be-misal, paida karney wala, baqi rakhney wala, waris, raahnumai karney wala, bahut bardasht karney wala.'' (Tirmizi, Behaqi), aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. (rawahu Tirmizi ( 3507 ( w al-Behaqi"
2289,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko in alfaz ke sath dua kartey huey suna : aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun ke to Allah hai, terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, yakta , be niaz hai, jiski aulad hai na waliden , aur na koi uska ham sar hai.'' to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ne Allah se uskey Isme-aazam ke tawassul se dua ki hai, jab us se us (yani Isme-Aazam) ke sath sawal kya jata hai to wo ata farmata hai, aur jab uskey sath dua ki jati hai to wo qubul farmata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3475 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 1493 ( ."
2290,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath masjid mein betha hua tha aur eik aadmi Namaz padh raha tha, usney kaha : aey Allah! main tujh se sawal karta hun ke her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin (bandon par) rehem karney wala, nematein ata karney wala, zamin w aasman ko adam se wajood bakhshney wala, aey izzat w ikram waley ! aey zinda aur qaaim rakhney waley! main tujh se sawal karta hun. ( ye sun kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us ( bandey ( ne Allah se uskey us Isme-aazam ke sath dua ki hai ke jab uskey sath us se dua ki jaey to wo qubul farmata hai, aur jab uskey sath us se sawal kya jaey to wo ata karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3544 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 1495 ( w Nasai ( 3 / ۵۲ padhi. 1301 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3858 ( ."
2291,"Hazrat Asma bint Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka Isme-Aazam un do aayaton mein hai, ( وَاِلٰھُکُمْ اِلٰہٌ وَاحِدٌ لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا ھُوَ الرَّحْمٰنُ الرَّحِیْمُ (aur sura Aale-Imran ke aaghaz ki aayat (الٓمٓ . اللہُ لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا ھُوَ الْحَیُّ الْقَیُّوْمُ) .'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3478 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 1496 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3855 ( w Darmi ( 2 / 450 padhi. 2392 ( ."
2292,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Yunus (Alaihissalam) jab machli ke pet mein they to unhoney un alfaz ke sath dua ki thi : ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ سُبْحَانَکَ اِنِّیْ کُنْتُ مِنَ الظَّالِمِیْنَ ( '' terey siwa koi mabud nahin, to paak hai, be-shak main hi zalimon mein se tha.'' koi musalman shakhs kisi mamley mein un alfaz ke sath dua karta hai to uski dua qubul ki jati hai.'' rawahu Ahmed (1 / 170 padhi. 1462 ( w Tirmizi ( 3505 ( ."
2293,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ishaa ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath masjid mein dakhil hua to eik aadmi buland aawaz se qirat kar raha tha, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya aap samajhtey hain ke ye ( aadmi ( riya kaar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, balke wo to ( ghaflat se zikr ki taraf ( ruju karney wala momin shakhs hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, us waqt Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) buland aawaz se qirat kar rahey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghor se unki qirat sunney lagey . phir Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) beth kar dua karney lagey to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ! main tujhey gawah bana kar kehta hun ke to Allah hai terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, yakta be niaz hai, jisney kisi ko janm diya na usey janm diya gaya, aur na hi koi uska hamsar hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usney Allah ke us Isme-Aazam ke sath sawal kya hai ke jab us se us ( Ism (ke sath sawal kya jata hai to wo ata karta hai, aur jab uskey sath us se dua ki jati hai to wo qubul farmata hai.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! maine aap se jo suna hai uskey mutalliq usey bata dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan ''maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat usey bata di to unhon ( Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujhey farmaya : aaj se tum merey bhai aur dost ho, tum ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat batai, ( rawahu rizeen w Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ( 1493 , 1494 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3857 ( w Tirmizi ( 3475 ( ."
2294,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaar kalmey, ( Subhanallah , Alhamdulillah , la Ilaah illallah (aur ( Allahu-akbar ( , behtareen kalam hain.'' ( rawahu muslim) . aur eik dusri riwayat mein : ''Allah ko chaar kalmey intehai pasand hain, ( Subhanallah , Alhamdulillah , la Ilaah illallah (aur ( Allahu-akbar ( , un mein se jisey bhi pehley padho wo tumharey liye Muzir nahin.''"
2295,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ , وَالْحَمْدُلِلہِ , وَلَا اِلَٰہ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَکْبَرُ ( , padh lena mujhey puri kaeynat (ke mil janey ( se ziyada pasand hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2296,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs din mein so martaba ( سُبْحَان اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ ( padhta hai to uskey gunah, chahey samandar ki jhaag jitney hun, maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6405 w Muslim"
2297,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh w Sham so martaba ( سُبْحَان اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ ( padhta hai to qiyamat ke din us se koi shakhs behtar nahin hoga bajuz uskey jisney us jitna ya us se ziyada martaba padha hoga .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari لم اجدہ w Muslim"
2298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do kalmey : ( سُبْحَان اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ سُبْحَان اللہِ الْعَظِیْمِ ( zaban par halkay , meezaan mein bhari aur Rehman ko mehbub hain.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6682 w Muslim"
2299,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi rozaana hazar neki kamaaney se aajiz hai? '' to aap ki majlis mein shareek kisi ne arz kya, ham mein se koi hazar neki kaisey kama sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' so martaba ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ ( kehney se uskey liye hazar neki likhi jati hai ya uskey hazar gunah mita diye jatey hain.'' Muslim . aur unhi ki kitab mein Musa al-Johni ki tamam riwayaat mein) اَوْیُحَطُّ ( '' ya mita diye jatey hain, ke alfaz hain, abu-Bakar barqaani ne farmaya : aur is hadees ko Shoba abu-Awaana aur Yahya bin Saeed qattaan ne Musa se riwayat kya to unhoney ( وْیُحَطُّ (ke alfaz riwayat kiye hain yani alif ke baghair ''aur mita diye jatey hain.'' kitab Humedi mein bhi isi tarah hai. rawahu Muslim ."
2300,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya, kon sa kalam afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo Allah ne apney farishton ke liye muntakhab kya ( سُبْحَان اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ ( .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2301,"Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr padhney ke liye subh ke waqt unke paas se tashrif ley gaey jabkey wo apni jaey Namaz par thin, phir aap chaasht ke waqt unke paas tashrif laye to wo wahin bethi huin thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aap usi haalat mein rahen jis par maine aap ko chhoda tha? unhoney arz kya, ji haan, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine aap ke (paas se janey ke) baad teen kalmey chaar martaba padhey hain, agar unka , aap ke din bhar ke kahey huey kalmaat ke sath wazan kya jaey to wo un par bhari hongey : ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ عَدَدَ خَلْقِہِ وَرِضَا نَفْسِہِ , وَزِنَۃَ عَرْشِہِ , وَمِدَادَ کَلِمَاتِہِ ( paak hai Allah apni hamd ke sath apni makhluq ki tadaad, apney nafs ki raza, apney arsh ke wazan aur apney kalmaat ki roshnai ke barabar .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2302,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs din mein so martaba ye dua padhta hai : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat hai, usi ke liye her qism ki tareef hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai.'' to usey das ghulam azad karney ke barabar sawab milta hai, uskey liye so nekiyan likhi jati hain. uskey so gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, wo pura din Sham honey tak shetan se mehfooz rahega aur us se behtar koi shakhs nahin aaeyga magar wo jisney us se ziyada martaba padha hoga .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6403 w Muslim"
2303,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kar rahey they ke log buland aawaz se Allahu-akbar padhney lagey , jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logo ! apney aap par aasani karo, kyonkey tum kisi behrey ya ghayeb ko nahin pukar rahey balke tum to sunney dekhney wali zaat ko pukar rahey ho aur wo tumharey sath hai, aur jis zaat ko tum pukartey ho wo to tumhari sawari ki gardan se bhi tumharey ziyada qarib hai.'' Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aap ke peechey apney dil mein) لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( padh raha tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abdullah bin Qais ! kya main tumhen jannat ke khazaney ke mutalliq bataaun ?'' maine arz kya, kyon nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( '' gunah se bachna aur nekii karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6384 w Muslim"
2304,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ الْعَظِیْمِ وَبِحَمْدِہِ ( padhta hai to uskey liye jannat mein khajoor ka eik darkht laga diya jata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3464 ( ."
2305,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her subh eik aelan karney wala ( farishta ( aelan karta hai : munazzah w muqaddas badshah ki tasbih bayan karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3569 ( ."
2306,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se afzal zikr ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ (aur afzal dua ( اَلْحَمْدُلِلہِ ( hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3383 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3800 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 326 , al-ehsaan : 843 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 497 ( ."
2307,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' الحمد ( Allah ki tareef karna ( shukr ki choti hai, jo banda Allah ki hamd bayan nahin karta wo Allah ka shukr ada nahin karta .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 4395 ( المصنف abdur-Razzaaq ( 19574 ( ."
2308,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat sab se pehley un logon ko jannat ki taraf bulaya jaeyga jo khushhali aur tang haali mein Allah ki hamd bayan kartey hain.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein Shobil-emaan mein bayan ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 4373 , 4483 , 4484 ( w al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah ( 5 / 50 padhi. 1270 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 502 padhi. ۱۸۵۱ ( ."
2309,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya, parwardigar ! mujhey koi chiz sikha dey jiskey sath mein tera zikr kya karun ya main uskey sath tujh se dua kya karun. farmaya : Musa! ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( padha karo, unhoney arz kya : parwardigar ! terey sarey bandey usey padhtey hain, main to aisi chiz chahta hun jo merey sath khas ho. farmaya : Musa! agar saton aasman aur merey siwa jahan mein basney waley aur saton zameenein eik paldey mein rakh di jaeyn aur) لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( doosrey paldey mein rakh diya jaey to ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( un par bhari hoga.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( 5 / 54 , 55 padhi. 1273 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 2324 ( w al-Hakim (1 / ۵۲۸ , 1362 ( ."
2310,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَ اللہُ اَکْبَرُ ( kehta hai to uska rab uski tasdeeq farmata hai, aur farmata hai : merey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main sab se bada hun. aur jab ( banda ( kehta hai : Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin. to Allah farmata hai : merey akeley ke siwa koi mabud nahin, mera koi shareek nahin, aur jab wo kehta hai : Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, usi ki badshahat hai aur usi ke liye her qism ki hamd w tareef hai, to Allah farmata hai : merey siwa koi mabud nahin, badshahat aur hamd merey hi liye hai aur jab wo kehta hai : Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se hai, to Allah farmata hai : merey siwa koi mabud nahin, gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz meri hi tofiq se hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''jo shakhs apni bimari mein ye kalmaat padhey aur phir wo faut ho jaey to usey aag nahin chhueygi .'' ( rawahu Tirmizi ( 3430 ( w ibne-Maja ( 2794 ( w Nasai fi الکبری ( 986 ( ."
2311,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik aurat ke paas aaye . uskey samney khajoor ki guthliyaan ya kankariyaan padi hui thin aur wo un par tasbih padh rahi thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi chiz na bataaun jo tumharey liye us se aasan tar ya afzal hai?  وَ سُبْحَانَ اللہِ عَدَدَ مَا خَلَقَ . . . . . . . . وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ مِثْلَ ذَلِکَ Allah ke liye tasbih hai un chizon ki ginti ke barabar jo usney aasman mein takhleeq farmaain, Allah ke liye tasbih hai un chizon ki ginti ke barabar jo usney zamin mein paida farmaain, uskey liye tasbih hai un chizon ki ginti ke barabar jo unke darmiyan hain, aur Allah ke liye tasbih hai un chizon ki ginti ke barabar jo wo paida karney wala hai, aur Allah ke liye badai hai usi misl, Allah ke liye hamd hai usi misl , ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( usi misl aur) لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( usi misl .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3568 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 1500 ( ."
2312,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh w Sham so so martaba Subhanallah kehta hai to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney so Haj kya ho, jo shakhs so martaba subh aur so martaba Sham Alhamdulillah kehta hai to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney Allah ki raah mein so ghodey faraham kiye hun, jo shakhs subh w Sham so so martaba ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( padhta hai to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad se so ghulam azad kiye hun aur jo shakhs subh w Sham so so martaba ( اَللہُ اَکْبَرُ ( kehta hai to roze-qiyamat us se badh kar koi afzal amal lekar hazir nahin hoga magar wo shakhs jisney uskey misl ya us se ziyada (ye wazeefa) kya hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3471 ( ."
2313,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Subhanallah kehna nisf meezaan hai jabkey Alhamdulillah kehna usko bhar deta hai, aur) لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( kisi hijaab ya rukawat ke baghair Allah tak pahunch jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai aur iski sanad qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3518 , 3519 ("
2314,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi banda kabeera gunahon se bachtey huey ikhlas ke sath ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( kehta hai to uskey liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain yahan tak ke wo arsh tak pahunch jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3590 ( ."
2315,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shabe-Meraj Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) se meri mulaqat hui to unhoney farmaya : '' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! meri taraf se apni ummat ko salam kehna aur unhen batana ke jannat ki mitti bahut achi hai aur uska pani mitha hai lekin wo eik saaf maidan hai, aur) سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَ الْحَمْدُلِلہِ وَلَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَکْبَر ( kehna is mein darkht lagana hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees sanad ke lihaz se Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3462 ( w Ahmed ( 5 / 418 padhi. 23948 ( ."
2316,"Hazrat Yusra (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke muhaajaraat mein se thin bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen farmaya : '' ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ ( ) لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ (aur ( سُبْحَانَ الْمَلِکِ الْقُدُّوْسَ ( padhney ka iltizaam ( ehtimam ( karo aur unhen ungliyon ke poron par shumar karo kyonkey ( roze-qiyamat ( un se puchha jaeyga aur wo kalam karengey , ghafil na hona warna tumhen rehmat se mehroom kar diya jaeyga.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood . rawahu Tirmizi ( 3583 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 1501 ("
2317,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, mujhey koi kalam sikhaaein jisey mein padha karun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho لا الہ الا اللہ . . . . . . العزیز الحکیم ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, Allah bahut bada hai, Allah ke liye bahut ziyada hamd hai, paak hai Allah jahano ka parwardigar, gunahon se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ghalib hikmat waley ki tofiq hi se mumkin hai.'' us Erabi (dehati) ne arz kya, ye kalmaat to merey rab ke liye huey to merey liye kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho : aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey, mujh par rehem farma, mujhey hidayat nasib farma, mujhey rizq ata farma aur mujhey aafiyat mein rakh.'' raawi ko) عافنی (ke alfaz mein shak hai. rawahu Muslim ."
2318,"Hazrat Anas se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik darkht ke paas se guzrey jiskey pattey khushk ho chukey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par apni lathi maari to pattey gir padey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( الْحَمْدَلِلہِ , سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَلَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَکْبَرُ ( bandey ke gunah gira deta hai jaisey us darkht ke pattey gir rahey hain.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi ( 3533 ( w Ahmed ( 3 / 152 ( w Bukhari"
2319,"Hazrat Mak-hool , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( kasrat se padha karo, kyonkey wo jannat ka khazana hai.'' Mak-hool ne farmaya : jo shakhs ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ وَلَا مَنْجَاءَ مِنَ اللہِ اِلَّا اِلَیْہِ ( padhta hai to Allah us se sattar qism ki taklifen door farma deta hai aur un mein se sab se kam faqr hai. Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin, Mak-hool ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se nahin suna . rawahu Tirmizi ( 3601 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 2338 ( ."
2320,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( ninnanwey bimariyon ki dawa hai aur un mein se sab se halki bimari gham hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi al-Hakim (1 / 542 ( ."
2321,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisa kalma na bataaun, jo ke arsh ke nichey jannat ka khazana hai, aur wo ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( hai, Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ne itaat ikhtiyar kar li aur apney aap ko Allah ke supurd kar diya.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein dawaatul-Kabir mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi w Ahmed w Nasai al-Hakim (1 / 21 ( w Ahmed 2 / 520 ( w Nasai ( 358 ( w al-Hakim)"
2322,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ ( kehna makhluq ki ibadat hai, ( اَلْحَمْدُلِلہِ ( kalma shukr hai, ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( kalma ikhlas hai, ( اَللہُ اَکْبَرُ ( zamin w aasman ke khala ko bhar deta hai, aur jab banda ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( padhta hai to Allah Taala farmata hai : usney itaat ikhtiyar ki aur apney aap ko merey supurd kar diya. rawahu rizeen, ( لم اجدہ ( w rawahu al-Hakim (1 / 21 ( w Ahmed ( 2 / 297, 363, 335 , 355 , 403 ( ."
2323,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! main din mein sattar baar se ziyada Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun aur uskey huzur tauba karta hun.'' Bukhari 6307 ( ."
2324,"Hazrat Agharrul-Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey dil par parda sa aa jata hai aur main din mein so martaba Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2325,"Hazrat Agharrul-muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logo ! Allah ke huzur tauba karo, kyonkey main din mein so martaba Allah ke huzur tauba karta hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2326,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is hadees mein, jo wo Allah tabarak w taala se riwayat kartey hain, farmaya ke us ( Allah Taala ( ne farmaya : ''merey bando ! maine zulm karna apney ooper haram qarar diya hai, aur usey tumharey beech bhi haram kya hai, tum baham (aapas mein) zulm na karo, merey bando ! tum sab gumrah they siwaey uskey jisey main hidayat ata karun, tum mujh se hidayat talab karo main tumhen hidayat ata karunga, merey bando! tum sab bhookey they bajuz uskey jisey mein khilaaun, tum mujh se khana talab karo, main tumhen khilaaunga, merey bando! tum sab libas ke baghair they siwaey uskey jisey main libas ata karun, tum mujh se libas talab karo main tumhen libas ata karunga, merey bando! tum din raat khataeyn kartey ho, aur sarey gunah main maaf karta hun, tum mujh se maghfirat talab karo, main tumhen bakhsh dunga, merey bando! agar tum mujhey nuqsan pahunchana chaho to tum mujhey nuqsan nahin pahuncha saktey, aur agar tum mujhey faeyda pahunchana chaho to tum mujhey faeyda nahin pahuncha saktey. merey bando ! agar tum sab jin w insan us shakhs ki tarah ho jaao jo tum mein sab se ziyada muttaqi hai to us se meri badshahat mein kuch izafa nahin hoga, merey bando ! agar tum sab jin w insan us shakhs ki tarah ho jaao jo tum mein sab se ziyada faajir w gunahgar hai to us se meri badshahat mein zara kami nahin hogi, merey bando ! agar tum sab jin w insan eik maidan mein khadey ho kar mujh se sawal karo aur main her insan ki murad puri kar dun to us se merey khazanon mein sirf itni si kami aaeygi jaisey samandar mein sui dal kar nikal leney se samandar mein kami aati hai, merey bando ! ye tumharey aamaal hi hain jinhen maine mehfooz w shumar kar rakha hai, phir main ( roze-qiyamat ( unhi ke mutabiq pura pura badla dunga, jo shakhs khair w bhalai paey to wo Allah ka shukr ada karey aur jo shakhs uskey ilawa koi aur chiz paey to phir wo apney aap hi ko malamat karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2327,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bani-Israel main eik shakhs tha jo ninnanwey insan qatl kar chuka tha phir wo masla daryaft karney ke liye nikla to wo kisi raahib ke paas aaya aur us se masla puchha to usey kaha : kya uskey liye tauba ki koi gunjaaish hai? usney kaha : nahin, usney usko bhi qatl kar dala , aur phir masla poochhney laga to kisi aadmi ne usey bataya ke falan-falan basti chaley jaao, (wo us taraf chal diya) lekin usey raastey hi mein maut aa gaee to usney us waqt apna Sina aagey (basti) ki taraf badhaya, rehmat aur azab ke farishtey uskey mutalliq jhagadney lagey to Allah ne us (basti) ko hukm diya ke uskey qarib ho ja, aur us (basti ko jidhar se aa raha tha) ko hukm diya ke door ho ja, phir farmaya : un dono ka darmiyani fasla napo, pas (pemaaish karney par) wo eik baalisht barabar us (basti) ke qarib paya gaya ( jahan ja raha tha ( to usey bakhsh diya gaya .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 3470 w Muslim"
2328,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum gunah na karo to Allah tumhen (is duniya sey) ley jaey aur eik dusri qom ley aaye jo gunah karen, phir Allah se maghfirat talab karen to wo unhen maaf kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2329,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah raat ke waqt apna haath phelata hai taake din ke waqt gunah karney wala tauba kar ley, aur wo din ke waqt apna haath phelata hai taake raat ke waqt gunah karney wala tauba kar ley (aur ye silsila jari rehta hai) yahan tak ke Suraj maghrib ki taraf se tulu ho jaey (yani qiyamat tak).'' rawahu Muslim ."
2330,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda aetraaf kar leta hai phir tauba karta hai to Allah bhi (rehmat ke sath) is par ruju farmata hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4141 aur Muslim."
2331,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Suraj ke maghrib ki taraf tulu honey (yani qiyamat qaaim honey) se pehley pehley tauba kar li to Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2332,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah apney bandey ki tauba sey, jab wo uskey huzur tauba karta hai, us shakhs se bhi ziyada khush hota hai, jiski sawari kisi jangal bayaabaan mein us se door bhag gaee ho, jabke uskey khaney peeney ka saman bhi is par tha, wo sawari se mayus ho kar eik darkht ke saye taley let gaya kyonkey wo apni sawari se to mayus ho chuka tha, wo usi karb (baicheni) mein tha ke achcha dekhta hai ke sawari uskey paas khadi hai, usney uski mahaar (nakel) thaamee , phir shiddat farhat se kaha : aey Allah ! to mera banda hai aur main tera rab hun, aur shiddat farhat ki wajeh se wo ghalat keh betha.'' rawahu Muslim."
2333,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda gunah karta hai to kehta hai : rab ji ! main gunah kar betha hun to usey bakhsh dey , to uska rab farmata hai : kya mera banda janta hai ke uska koi rab hai jo gunah bakhshta hai aur uski wajeh se muwaakhiza (pakad) bhi kar sakta hai? maine apney bandey ko bakhsh diya, phir jis qadr Allah chahta hai wo shakhs gunah se baaz rehta hai, lekin phir gunah kar leta hai aur kehta hai, rab ji ! main gunah kar betha hun usey maaf farma dey, to Allah Taala farmata hai : kya mera banda janta hai ke uska eik rab hai jo gunah bakhsh sakta hai aur is par muwaakhiza (pakad) bhi kar sakta hai? maine apney bandey ko bakhsh diya, phir jis qadr Allah chahta hai wo baaz rehta hai, lekin phir gunah kar bethta hai to kehta hai, rab ji ! main eik aur gunah kar betha hun, mujhey maaf farma dey , to Allah Taala farmata hai, kya mera banda janta hai ke uska eik rab hai jo gunah maaf kar sakta hai aur is par muwaakhiza (pakad) bhi kar sakta hai? maine apney bandey ko maaf kar diya, wo jo chahey so karey.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7507 aur Muslim"
2334,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hadees bayan ki ke kisi aadmi ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Allah falan shakhs ko maaf nahin kerega, to Allah Taala ne farmaya : wo kon hai jo mujh par qism uthata hai ke main falan shakhs ko maaf nahin karunga, maine usey to maaf kar diya aur terey aamaal zaya kar diye.'' ya jaisey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
2335,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saiyadul-istighfaar yun hai ke tum kaho : aey Allah ! to mera rab hai terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to ne mujhey paida farmaya , main tera banda hun, main apni istataat ke mutabiq terey ehad aur wadey par qaaim hun, maine jo kuchh kiya uskey shar se teri panah chahta hun, aap ke jo inaamat mujh par hain main unka iqrar karta hun, aur apney gunahon ka bhi iqrar karta hun, mujhey bakhsh dey , kyonkey sirf tu hi gunah maaf kar sakta hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs in kalimaat par yaqin rakhtey huey din ke waqt unhen padhey aur wo usi roz Sham honey se pehley faut ho jaey to wo shakhs jannati hai, aur jo shakhs in kalimaat par yaqin rakhtey huey Sham ke waqt inhen padhey aur wo subah honey se pehley faut ho jaey to wo jannati hai.'' Bukhari (2306)."
2336,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : ibne-Adam ! jab tak to mujh se dua karta rahega aur mujh se (bakhshish ki) ummid rakhega to main tumhen maaf karta rahunga chahey (chaahe) tumharey gunah kitney hi ziyada kyon na hon iski mujhey koi parwah nahin, ibne-Adam ! agar terey gunah aasman ke abr (kinaron) tak pahunch jaeyn , phir to mujh se maghfirat talab karey to main tumhen maaf kar dunga aur mujhey iski koi parwah nahin, ibne-Adam ! agar to zamin ke bharney ke barabar gunah karkey merey paas aaye lekin to ne merey sath kisi ko shareek na thehraya ho, to main itni hi miqdaar mein maghfirat lekar tumharey paas aaunga.'' rawahu Tirmizi (3540)."
2337,"Hazrat Imam Ahmed aur Imam Darmi ne isey Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 167,  21804 , 5 / 172,  21505 (aur Darmi ( 2 / 322, 2791)."
2338,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : jo shakhs ye janta hai ke main gunah maaf karney par qadir hun to main usey maaf kar deta hun, aur mujhey uski koi parwah nahin, ba-sharte-ke usney merey sath kisi ko shareek na thehraya ho.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( 14 / 388 padhi. 4191 ( w al-Hakim (4 / 262 )."
2339,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs istighfar par dawaam (hameshgi) ikhtiyar kar leta hai to Allah uski her tangi door farma deta hai, her gham se khulaasi deta hai aur usey aisi jagah se rizq ata farmata hai jahan se usey guman bhi nahin hota.'' rawahu Ahmed (1 / 247 padhi. 2243 ), Abu-Dawood ( 1518 (aur ibne-Maja ( 3819 ( ."
2340,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maghfirat talab karta hai wo gunah par dawaam (hameshgi) ikhtiyar karney walon mein sey nahin chahey wo din mein sattar martaba wohi gunah dohraaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi (3559 (aur Abu-Dawood ( 1514 ( ."
2341,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Adam (Alaihissalam) ki sari aulad khatakar hai, aur behtar khatakar wo hain jo tauba karney waley hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2499 ), ibne-Maja ( 2451 ), Darmi ( 2 / 303 padhi. 2730 ( aur  al-Haakim (4 / 244 )."
2342,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab momin koi gunah karta hai to uskey dil par eik siyah nukta lag jata hai, agar wo tauba kar ley aur maghfirat talab kar ley to uska dil saaf kar diya jata hai, aur agar wo gunah mein badhta chala jaey to wo nuktey bhi badhtey chaley jatey hain yahan tak ke wo uskey dil par ghalib aa jatey hain, yehi wo zang hai jis ka Allah Taala ne zikr kiya hai : ''hergiz nahin, balke unke aamaal ki wajeh se unke dilon par zang hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 297 padhi. 7939 ), Tirmizi ( 3334 ), ibne-Maja ( 4244 ), ibne-Hibban ( 1771 , 2448 (aur al-Haakim ( 2 / 517 ( ."
2343,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak bandey ki rooh hulqoom tak na pahunchey , Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3537 ), ibne-Maja ( 4253 ), ibne-Hibban ( 2449 (aur al-Hakim (4 / 257)."
2344,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shetan ne kaha : rab ! teri izzat ki qism ! jab tak terey bandon ki roohen unke jism mein hain mein unhen gumrah karta rahunga , to Shan Wale rab ne farmaya : mujhey apni izzat aur jalal aur apni buland makaani ki qism ! jab tak wo mujh se maghfirat talab kartey rahengey , main unhen maaf karta rahunga .'' ( rawahu Ahmed ( 3 / 29, 11257 , 41, 11387 ( w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( 5 / 76 , 77, 1293 (aur al-Haakim (4 / 261,  7672 ( ."
2345,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne maghrib ki taraf tauba ke liye eik darwaza banaya jis ka arz sattar saal ki masafat (doori) ke barabar hai, aur jab tak Suraj uski taraf se tulu nahin hota wo (tauba ka darwaza) khula hua hai, aur yehi wo Shan Wale Allah ka farman hai : ''jis roz terey rab ki baaz nishaniyan aa jaeyngi to kisi nafs ka us waqt eman lana faeeda-mand nahin hoga jo pehley eman nahin laya tha.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3536 (aur ibne-Maja ( 4070 ( ."
2346,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hijrat munqata'' (hijrat khatam) nahin hogi yahan tak ke tauba ka darwaza band ho jaey aur tauba ka darwaza band  nahin hoga yahan tak ke Suraj maghrib se tulu ho jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 99 padhi. 17030 ), Abu-Dawood ( 3479 (aur Darmi ( 2 / 240,  2516)."
2347,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bani Israel ke do aadmi eik doosrey ke dost they, un mein se eik intehai ibadat guzar tha jabkey doosra kehta tha : main gunah gaar hun, ye usey kehta : apni rawish se baaz aa jaao , to wo kehta : mera maamla merey rab par chhod do , yahan tak ke usney eik roz usey gunah kartey huey paya to usney usey bahut bura samajhtey huey kaha : baaz aa jaao , usney kaha : mujhey merey rab par chhod do , kya tum mujh par nigraan bana kar bhejey gaey ho? to us (ibadat guzar) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Allah tumhen kabhi maaf kerega na kabhi tumhen jannat mein dakhil kerega, isliye Allah ne un dono ki taraf farishta bheja to usney un dono ki roohen qabz kar lein, aur wo dono uskey paas ikhattey ho gaey to Allah Taala ne gunah gaar shakhs se farmaya : meri rehmat ke sath jannat mein dakhil ho ja , aur doosrey se farmaya : kya tum taqat rakhtey ho ke tum meri rehmat ko merey bandey se rok do? wo arz karta hai, nahin, merey rab ! Allah Taala farmata hai : usey jahannam mein ley jaao.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 323,  8275 , 2 / 362, 8734 ), Abu-Dawood ( 4901 (aur tafseer ibn Kasir ( 2 / 265 ( ."
2348,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye aayat padhtey huey suna : ''merey wo bandey jinhonne apni jaanon par zulm kiya hai Allah ki rehmat se mayus na hon kyonkey Allah tamam gunah maaf kar deta hai.'' aur wo parwah nahin karta.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur Sharahus-sunnah mein یقرا ke badley یقول ke alfaz hain. ( rawahu Ahmed ( 6 / 459,  28148 ), Tirmizi ( 3237 (aur fi Sharahus-sunnah ( 14 / 384 padhi. 4186)."
2349,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ka farman : ( اِلَّا اللَّمَمَ (ke barey mein bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! agar to maaf kar dey to sabhi gunah maaf kar dey , aur tera kon sa banda hai jo sagheera gunah nahin karta.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3274 (aur al-Haakim ( 2 / 469 , 470 ( ."
2350,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : merey bando ! tum sab gumrah ho magar jisey main hidayat ata farma dun, tum mujh se hidayat talab karo, tum sab fuqra ho magar jisey main ghani kar dun, tum mujh se apna rizq talab karo, aur tum sab gunah-gaar ho magar jisey main bacha lun , tum mein se jisey ilm ho ke main maghfirat karney par qadir hun aur wo mujh se maghfirat talab karey to main usey bakhsh deta hun aur main parwah nahin karta , aur agar tumhara awwal aur aakhir , tumharey zinda aur murda , tumharey jawan aur tumharey boodhey , sarey merey bandon mein se us shakhs jaisey ho jaeyn jo sab se ziyada muttaqi hai to us se meri badshahat mein machchhar ke par jitna bhi izafa nahin hoga, aur agar tumhara awwal aur aakhir , tumharey zinda aur murda aur tumharey jawan aur boodhey sab , merey bandon mein se us shakhs jaisey ho jaeyn jo ke sab se ziyada bad-naseeb aur gumrah hai to us se meri badshahat mein machchhar ke par ke barabar bhi kami nahin aaeygi , aur agar tumhara awwal aur aakhir , tumharey zinda aur murda aur tumharey jawan aur boodhey sab eik maidan mein ikhattey ho jaeyn , phir tum mein se her insan ji bhar kar mang ley aur main tum mein se her saail ko de-dun to us se meri badshahat mein itna hi farq aaeyga jaisey tum mein se koi samandar ke paas se guzrey aur wo us main eik sooi dubo kar bahar nikal ley , isliye ke main sakhi daata hun, jo chahta hun kar guzarta hun, mera ata karna kalam hai aur mera azab karna bhi kalam hai, kisi chiz ke barey mein mera hukm to bas itna hi hai ke jab main irada karta hun to main uskey barey mein yehi kehta hun ke , ho ja , to wo ho jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 154 padhi. 21695 ), Tirmizi ( 2495 (aur ibne-Maja (4257)."
2351,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney ye aayat padhi : '' wo ( Allah Taala ( ehle taqwa aur ehle maghfirat hai.'' to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhara rab farmata hai : main us laaiq hun ke mujh se dara jaey, jo shakhs mujh se darta hai to phir main uska ehl hun ke main usey bakhsh dun.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2352,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik majlis mein so martaba ye farmatey huey : ''merey rab! mujhey bakhsh dey, mujh par ruju farma, be-shak to tauba qubul karney wala bakhshney wala hai.'' shumar kya kartey they. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
2353,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke azad karda ghulam Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke potey Bilal bin Yasar bayan kartey hain, merey walid (Yasar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne merey dada (Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) : ko farmatey huey suna! ''jo shakhs ye dua padhey : (astaghfirullah . . . . . . w-atubu ilaih) ''main Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo zinda aur qaaim rakhney wala hai, aur main uskey huzur tauba karta hun, to usey bakhsh diya jata hai chaahey wo maidane-jihad se farar hua ho.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. lekin Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein Hilal bin Yasar hai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
2354,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall Saleh bandey ka jannat mein darja buland farmata hai to wo arz karta hai : rab ji! ye mujhey kaisey hasil hua? to wo farmata hai : terey bachey (beta, beti) ke terey liye duaae-maghfirat karney ki wajeh se.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2355,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maiyat qabr mein, doobtey huey fariyad karney waley ki tarah hai, wo baap ya maa ya bhai ya dost ki taraf se pahunchney wali dua ki muntazir rehti hai, jab wo usey pahunch jati hai to wo uskey liye duniya w jo kuch usmein hai usse behtar hoti hai, aur be-shak Allah Taala ( duniya ( walon ki duaaon se ehle quboor par pahadon jitni rahmatein nazil farmata hai, aur zindon ka mardon ke liye tohfa unke liye maghfirat talab karna hai.'' rawahu al-Behaqi ."
2356,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ke liye khushkhabri ho jo apney namae-aamaal mein bahut ziyada istighfar paey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
2357,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kartey they : ''aey Allah! mujhey un logon mein shamil farma ke jab wo neki kartey hain to khush ho jatey hain aur jab koi ghalati kar bethtey hain to maghfirat talab kartey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi.
2358,"Hazrat Haris bin Suwed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamen do hadisein bayan kin. un mein se eik Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se (Marfoo) aur dusri apni taraf se (moquf) , farmaya : '' momin apney gunahon ko yun samajhta hai jaisey wo kisi pahad ke nichey betha ho aur wo darta hai ke wo is par gir padega, jabkey faajir shakhs apney gunahon ko yun samajhta hai jaisey makkhi uski naak par beth gaee ho, phir unhoney haath ke isharay se apney aap se makkhi uda kar dikhai, phir unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna Allah apney momin bandey ki tauba se us shakhs se bhi ziyada khush hota hai, jo kisi mohlik bayaban mein padaaw daley, uskey sath uski sawari ho jis par uska khana peena ho, usney apna sar rakha aur so gaya, jab wo bedaar hua to uski sawari kahin ja chuki thi, usney usey talash kya yahan tak ke jab garmi, piyas ya jo Allah ne chaha is par shadeed ho gaee to usney kaha : main apni usi pehli jagah par wapis jata hun aur so jata hun yahan tak ke main faut ho jaaun, usney apney bazu par apna sar rakha taake wo faut ho jaey, wo bedaar hua to uski sawari uskey paas khadi thi aur uskey khaney peeney ka saman bhi is par mojud tha, Allah momin bandey ki tauba se us aadmi se bhi ziyada khush hota hai jisey apni sawari aur apna zaade-raah milney par khushi hoti hai.'' Imam Muslim ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se faqat marfoo riwayat kya hai, jabkey Imam Bukhari ne ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se usey moquf bhi riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim w Bukhari."
2359,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah gunah mein mubtala bahut ziyada tauba karney waley momin bandey ko pasand karta hai.''"
2360,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''is aayat'' merey bando! jinhon ne apni jaanon par zulm kya Allah ki rehmat se mayus na hona '' ke badley puri duniya ka mil jana bhi mujhey pasand nahin .'' kisi aadmi ne arz kya, to jisney shirk kya ho? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey, phir aapney teen martaba farmaya : ''sun lo! jisney shirk kya ho.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2361,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala hijaab waqey honey se pehley tak apney bandey ko bakhshta rehta hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! hijaab kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi jaan haalate-shirk mein faut ho.'' teeno ahadis Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kin aur Imam Behaqi ne aakhiri hadees '' kitabul-ba's wannushur'' main riwayat ki hai. rawahu Ahmed."
2362,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is haal mein Allah ke sath mulaqat karey ke wo duniya mein kisi ko Allah ke barabar qarar na deta ho, phir is par pahadon jitney bhi gunah hun to Allah usko maaf farma dega .'' rawahu al-Behaqi ."
2363,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gunah se tauba karney wala us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney koi gunah kya hi na ho.'' ( ibne-Maja , Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( , aur farmaya : is mein nahraani ka tafarrud hai, aur wo majhool hai. jabkey Sharahus-sunnah mein Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se moquf riwayat hai, farmaya : nadaamat se tauba murad hai, aur tauba karney wala us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney koi gunah kya hi na ho. rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi ."
2364,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne makhluq ko paida farmaya to usney eik kitab likhi jo uskey paas arsh par hai, ke meri rehmat merey ghazab par sabqat ley gaee.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''merey ghazab par ghalib aa gaee.'' muttafaq aleh."
2365,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki so rahmatein hain, un mein se eik rehmat jinnon, insanon, Haiwaanon aur zahreeley janweron mein utaar di jiskey zariey wo baham (aapas mein) shafqat aur rehem kartey hain, usi wajeh se wehshi janwer apney bachey par shafqat karta hai, jabkey Allah ne ninnanwey rahmatein apney paas rakhi hain jinkey zariey wo roze-qiyamat apney bandon par rehem farmaeyga .'' muttafaq aleh."
2366,"Hazrat sahih Muslim mein Salman se marwi (bayan) riwayat isi tarah hai, aur uskey aakhir mein hai, farmaya : ''pas jab roze-qiyamat hoga to wo us rehmat se un ( ninnanwey rahmaton) ko mukammal ( so ( farmaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2367,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar momin ko Allah ke azab ka pata chal jaey to koi bhi uski jannat ki ummid na rakhey, aur agar kafir ko Allah ki rehmat ka pata chal jaey to koi uski jannat se na-umeed na ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
2368,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat tumharey jootey ke tasmey se bhi ziyada tum se qarib hai aur jahannam bhi usi tarah.'' Bukhari ."
2369,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aadmi ne, jisney kabhi koi neki nahin ki thi, apney ehle khana se kaha, jabkey dusri riwayat mein hai : kisi aadmi ne bahut gunah kiye they, pas jab uski maut ka waqt aaya to usney apney beton ko wasiyat ki, jab wo faut ho jaey to usey jala dena, phir us (raakh) ke nisf hissey ko khushki mein aur uskey nisf ko samandar mein baha dena, Allah ki qasam! agar Allah ne us (mujh) par tangi ki to wo usey aisa azab dega ke usney tamam jahan walon mein se kisi ko aisa azab nahin diya hoga, pas jab wo faut ho gaya to unhoney uski wasiyat ke mutabiq amal kya, pas Allah ne samandar ko hukm diya to usney us hissey ko jo ke uskey andar tha, jama kar diya, aur khushki (zameen) ko hukm diya to usney bhi us hissey ko jo uskey andar tha, jama kar diya, phir us ( Allah taalaa) ne us (aadmi) se farmaya : tum ne aisey kyon kya? usney arz kya : rab ji! terey dar ki wajeh sey, jabkey to janta hai, pas usney usey maaf kar diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
2370,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch qaidi aaye, un qaidiyon main eik aurat thi jiski chhaati se doodh nikal raha tha, wo daudti phirti thi, jab wo qaidiyon mein koi bacha paati to usey pakad kar apney pet se lagaati aur usey doodh pilati, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen farmaya : ''kya tum guman kar saktey ho ye aurat apney bachey ko aag mein phenk degi?'' ham ne arz kya, nahin, agar wo usey na phainkney par qadir ho, (to wo nahin phenkegi) , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah apney bandon par is aurat se bhi ziyada meharban hai jitna ye apney bachey par meharban hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2371,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi shakhs ke aamaal usey najat nahin dilaaeingey.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aap bhi nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aur main bhi nahin, magar ye ke Allah apni rehmat se mujhey dhanpley, durusti ke sath amal kartey raho, miyaana rawi ikhtiyar karo, subh w Sham aur raat ke kuch hissey mein ibadat karo, aetidaal ka khayal rakho, aetidaal ka khayal rakho, is tarah tum manzil pa logey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2372,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ka amal usey jannat mein dakhil kara sakta hai na usey jahannam se bacha sakta hai aur main bhi Allah ki rehmat ke sath ( jannat mein jaaunga).'' rawahu Muslim."
2373,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda musalman ho jata hai aur apney Islam ko behtar banata hai to Allah uskey sabiqa tamam gunah maaf kar deta hai, aur us ( Islam qubul karney (ke baad phir badla shuru ho jata hai, neki ka badla das guna se saat so guna tak badha diya jata hai, jabkey burai ka badla uskey misl hota hai siwaey iske ke Allah us se darguzar farmaai .'' Bukhari ."
2374,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne nekiyan aur buraiyan likhi hain, jis shakhs ne kisi neki ka irada kya lekin usey kya nahin to Allah usey apney paas uskey haq main eik mukammal neki likh leta hai, agar wo uska irada karey aur usey kar bhi ley to Allah usey apney paas uskey haq mein das guna se saat so guna aur us se bhi badha kar likh leta hai, aur jo shakhs burai karney ka irada karey lekin usey karey nahin to Allah usey apney paas uskey haq main eik kamil neki likh leta hai, lekin agar wo us ( burai (ka irada karey aur usey kar guzrey to Allah usey uskey haq main eik hi burai likhtaa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2375,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs gunah karta hai aur phir nek amal karta hai uski misal us shakhs jaisi hai jis par tang zireh ho jisney uska gala ghoont rakha ho, phir wo koi nek amal karta hai to eik kadi khul gaee, phir usney dusri neki ki to dusri kadi khul gaee yahan tak ke wo khul kar zamin par aa rahi.'' ( rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2376,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par waaz w nasihat kartey huey suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''jo shakhs apney rab ke huzur khada honey se dar gaya uskey liye do jannaten hain.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar-che wo zina aur chori karey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dusri martaba farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney rab ke huzur khada honey se dar gaya uskey liye do jannaten hain.'' maine dusri martaba arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar-che wo zina aur chori karey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teesri martaba farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney rab ke huzur khada honey se dar gaya uskey liye do jannaten hain.'' to maine bhi teesri martaba arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar-che wo zina aur chori karey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' agar-che abu-Darda ki naak khaak aalud ho.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
2377,"Hazrat AamirRam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, is beech mein ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke eik aadmi aaya, is par chadar thi aur uskey haath mein koi chiz thi jisey usney lapet rakha tha, usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main darakhton ke jhund ke paas se guzra to maine is mein parindon ke bachon ki aawazen sunen to maine unhen pakad liya , aur unhen apni chadar mein rakh liya , phir unki maa aai aur merey sar par chakkar laganey lagi , maine un ( bachon ( se parda hataaya to wo bhi un par aa giri, maine unhen apni chadar mein lapet liya, aur wo ye merey paas hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen rakho.'' usney unhen rakha to unki maa bhi unke sath hi rahi, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum bachon ki maa ke apney bachon ke sath rehem karney par tajjub kartey ho? us zaat ki qism jisney mujhey haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! Allah apney bandon ke sath , bachon ki maa ke apney bachon ke sath rehem karney se bhi ziyada rehem karney wala hai, unhen wahin ja kar rakh aao jahan se tum ne unhen uthaya tha.'' aur unki maa bhi unke sath thi, wo ( aadmi ( unhen wapis ley gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2378,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kisi ladaai mein shareek they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi qom ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''kon log ho?'' unhoney arz kya, ham musalman hain, wahan eik aurat handiya ke nichey aag jala rahi thi, aur uskey sath uska beta tha, jab aag ki tapish tez hoti to wo us bachey ko door kar leti, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya : aap Allah ke Rasool hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' usney arz kya, merey waliden aap par qurban hon, kya Allah sab se badh kar rehem karney wala nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyon nahin.'' phir usney arz kya, kya Allah apney bandon par, maa ke apney bachey par rehem karney se ziyada rehem karney wala nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyon nahin.'' usney arz kya : phir maa to yaqinan apney bachey ko aag mein nahin dal sakti, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sar jhuka kar roney lagey, phir aapney uski taraf sar utha kar farmaya : ''Allah apney bandon mein se sirf sarkash logon ko azab dega aur wo sarkash bhi aisey jo Allah ke khilaf sarkashi kartey hain aur) لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ ( kehney se inkar kar detey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2379,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' banda Allah ki razamandi talash karta hai, wo usi koshish mein laga rehta hai to Allah azz-w-jall Jibrael se farmata hai : mera falan banda mujhey razi karney ki koshish karta hai, sun lo meri rehmat is par hai, to Jibrael farmatey hain : Allah ki rehmat falan shakhs par hai, phir haameleen arsh yehi kehtey hain aur phir unke Aas paas waley yehi kehtey hain, yahan tak ke saton aasman waley yehi aelan kartey hain, phir uski wajeh se wo (rehmat ( zamin par utarti hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
2380,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Allah Taala ke us farman : ''un mein se koi apni jaan par zulm karney wala hai, aur koi miyaana ro hai aur koi nekiyon mein badhney wala hai.'' ke barey mein riwayat kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo sab jannati hain.'' rawahu al-Behaqi."
2381,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Sham kartey to farmatey : '' ham ne Sham ki aur Allah ki tamam badshahat ne Sham ki, her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, uskey liye badshahat hai aur usi ke liye hamd hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, aey Allah ! main tujh se us raat ki bhalai maangta hun aur jo is mein hai uski bhalai maangta hun, aur uskey shar se aur jo is mein hai uskey shar se teri panah chahta hun. aey Allah! main kaahili, budhapey, budhapey ki kharabi, duniya ke fitney aur qabr ke azab se teri panah chahta hun.'' aur jab aap subh kartey to bhi yehi kehtey : ''ham ne aur Allah ki badshahat ne subh ki.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''rab ji ! main tujh se aag ke azab aur azabe-qabr se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2382,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt apney bistar par tashrif latey to aap apna haath apney rukhsaar ke nichey rakhtey, phir ye dua padhtey : ''aey Allah ! main terey hi naam se marta aur zinda hota hun.'' aur jab aap bedaar hotey to ye dua padhtey : '' her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney hamen maarney ke baad zinda kya aur usi ki taraf lot kar jana hai.'' Bukhari."
2383,aur Muslim ne Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees bayan ki hai. rawahu Muslim.
2384,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney bistar par aaye to wo ( pehley (apney izaar ke kinarey se apney bistar ko jhaadey, kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uskey baad is par kon si chiz aai, phir wo ye dua padhey : merey parwardigar! terey naam ke sath maine apney pehlu ko rakha , aur terey naam ke sath hi uthaunga, agar to meri jaan qabz kar ley to phir is par rehem farmana, aur agar to usey chhod dey to uski is tarah hifazat farmana jaisey to apney Saleh bandon ki hifazat farmata hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''phir wo apney daain pehlu par letey phir dua padhey : bismik.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' apney kapdey ke kinarey se teen martaba jhaadey aur kahey agar to meri jaan qabz kar ley to usey bakhsh dena .'' muttafaq aleh."
2385,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney bistar par aatey to aap daain karwat let'tey, phir ye dua padhtey : ''aey Allah ! maine apni jaan terey supurd kar di, apna chehra teri taraf mutawajjeh kar diya, apna maamla terey supurd kar diya aur apni pusht teri taraf jhukaai. aur ye sab kuch tera shoq rakhtey huey aur tujh se dartey huey kya, terey siwa koi panah gaah hai na maqam najat, mein teri kitab par eman laya jisey to ne naazil farmaya, aur terey Nabi par eman laya jisey to ne bheja .'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye kalmaat padhey aur phir usi raat faut ho jaey to wo fitrat (yani Islam ( par faut hoga.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aadmi se farmaya : ''aey falan! jab tum apney bistar par letnaa chaho to Namaz ka sa wuzu karo . phir apney daain pehlu par leto , phir ye dua padho : aey Allah ! maine apni jaan terey supurd ki . . . . . . yani mukammal dua padhi .'' farmaya : ''agar tum usi raat faut ho gaey to tum fitrat (yani Islam ( par faut hogey aur agar subh ki to tum khair w bhalai paaogey .'' muttafaq aleh."
2386,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney bistar par aatey to ye dua padhtey : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney hamen khana khilaya, pilaya, wo hamarey liye kafi ho gaya aur hamen thikana ata farmaya, kitney hi log hain jinhen koi kifaayat karney wala hai na thikana deney wala hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2387,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas us takleef ki shikayat lekar gaeen jo unhen chakki peesney se hui thi, aur unhen pata chala tha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch ghulam aaye hain, lekin unki aap se mulaqat na ho saki to unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se apney aaney ka maqsad bayan kya, jab aap tashrif laye to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aap ko bataya , Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aap aisey waqt mein hamarey paas tashrif laye ke ham apney bistaron par let chukey they, ham uthney lagey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni jagah par letey raho.'' phir aap hamarey darmiyan beth gaey yahan tak ke maine aap ke paaon ki thandak apney pet par mehsus ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen us chiz sey, jiska tum ne sawal kya hai, behtar chiz bataaun? jab tum apney bistar par jaao to tentis martaba ( Subhanallah ( tentis martaba ( Alhamdulillah (aur chauntees martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( padh liya karo, wo tumharey liye, khaadim ke mil janey se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2388,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se eik khaadim ka mutalba karney aap ke paas aain to aapney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi chiz na bataaun jo ke khaadim se behtar hai, ke tum her Namaz aur sotey waqt tentis martaba'' Subhanallah '' tentis martaba '' Alhamdulillah '' aur chauntees martaba ''Allah akbar '' padh liya keren.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2389,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh kartey to ye dua padhtey : ''aey Allah! ham ne teri hi tofiq se subh ki, teri hi tofiq se Sham ki, teri hi tofiq se zinda hain, teri hi tofiq se marengey aur teri hi taraf lotna hai.'' aur jab aap Sham kartey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah! ham ne teri hi tofiq se Sham ki aur teri hi tofiq se subh ki, teri hi tofiq se zinda hain aur terey hi naam par marengey aur teri hi taraf uth kar jana hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
2390,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey koi aisa wazeefa bataaeyn jisey mein subh Sham padha karun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kaho, aey Allah ! ghaib w hazir ko janney waley! zamin w aasman ko paida karney waley ! her chiz ke rab aur malik! main gawahi deta hun ke terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur main apney nafs ke shar, shetan ke shar aur uskey shirk se teri panah chahta hun.'' jab tum subh karo, jab Sham karo aur jab apney bistar par aao to ye kalmaat kaha karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi."
2391,"Hazrat Aban bin Usman bayan kartey hain, maine apney walid (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bayan kartey huey suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs her roz subh w Sham teen-teen martaba ye dua padhey to usey koi chiz takleef nahin pahunchaeygi : ''Allah ke naam ke sath jiskey naam ke sath zamin w aasman ki koi chiz takleef nahin pahuncha sakti aur wo sunney wala janney wala hai.'' Aban ko falij ho gaya to wo aadmi (jisko unhoney hadees sunai thi tajjub ke sath) unki taraf dekhney laga to Aban ne usey kaha : tum meri taraf kya dekhtey ho? rahi hadees to wo wesay hi hai jaisey maine tumhen bayan ki hai, lekin maine aaj usey padha nahin taake Allah apni taqdir mujh par nafiz kar sakey. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''usey subh honey tak koi naa-gahani aafat nahin aaeygi aur jo shakhs subh ke waqt usey padhey to Sham honey tak usey koi na-gahaani aafat nahin aaeygi.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Abu-Dawood."
2392,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Sham kartey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''ham ne aur Allah ke mulk ne Sham ki, her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, uskey liye badshahat hai, usi ke liye hamd hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, merey rab! main us raat ki behtari aur uskey baad aaney wali raaton ki behtari ka sawal karta hun aur us raat ke shar se aur uskey baad aaney wali raaton ke shar se teri panah chahta hun, merey rab! main kahili, budhapey ki kharabi ya kufr ki kharabi se teri panah chahta hun.'' eik aur dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main budhapey aur takabbur ki kharabi sey, merey rab ! main aag ke azab se teri panah chahta hun.'' aur jab aap subh kartey to bhi aisey hi dua kartey they : ''ham ne aur Allah ke mulk ne subh ki.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi. aur unki riwayat mein : ''kufr ki kharabi se.'' ke alfaz mazkur nahin. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi."
2393,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi lakhte-jigar se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen dua sikhaya kartey they, aap farmatey : ''jab tum subh karo to ye dua padho : paak hai Allah apni hamd ke sath, sarey kaam Allah ki tofiq se hotey hain, jo Allah chahey wo hota hai, aur jo na chahey, nahin hota. mein janta hun ke Allah her chiz par qadir hai, aur be-shak Allah ne ilm ke zariey her chiz ka ehata kar rakha hai.'' jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye kalmaat kahey to wo Sham tak mehfooz rehta hai aur jo shakhs Sham ke waqt ye kalmaat kahey to wo subh honey tak mehfooz rehta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2394,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye aayaat padhey : ( فَسُبْحَانَ اللہِ . . . . . . . . وَکَذَالِکَ تُخْرَجُوْنَ ( [ ۳۰ / Rome : ۱۷ . ۱۹ ] ( '' pas tum Allah ki tasbih bayan karo jab Sham ho aur jis waqt subh ho, aur aasmano aur zamin mein uski hamd hai, aur uski tasbih karo teesrey pahar bhi aur jab do-pehar ho, wo jandaar ko be jaan se nikalta hai, aur be jaan ko jandaar se bahar lata hai, aur zamin ko uskey murda aur khushk ho janey ke baad zinda kar deta hai aur isi tarah tum bhi usi ki taraf nikaley jaaogey.'' to us roz jo us se nek amal chhoot gaya hoga wo un kalmaat ke kehney se pa lega, aur jo shakhs ye kalmaat Sham ke waqt kahega to us se jo amal us raat mein reh jaeyga to wo un kalmaat ke zariey unka tadaaruk kar lega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2395,"Hazrat abu-Ayash (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye dua padhta hai : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat hai, usi ke liye her qism ki hamd hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai.'' uskey liye aulad Ismail (Alaihissalam) se das ghulam azad karney ke barabar sawab hai, uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain, us se das gunah mita diye jatey hain, uskey das darjaat buland kar diye jatey hain aur pura din Sham honey tak uskey liye shetan se bachaaw aur tahaffuz ho jata hai. aur agar wo unhen Sham ke waqt padhey to bhi uskey liye itna hi ajr hai yahan tak ke wo subh karey.'' kisi aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khuwab mein dekha to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! abu-Ayash aap se is tarah hadees bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' abu-Ayash ne sach kaha .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
2396,"Hazrat Haris bin Muslim tamimi apney walid se aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aahisatagi se un se farmaya : ''jab tum namaze-Maghrib se farigh ho jaao to kisi se baat karney se pehley saat martaba ye dua padho : ''aey Allah ! mujhey aag se bacha ley.'' agar tum ne ye dua padh li aur usi raat faut ho jaao to tumharey liye us ( aag ( se khulaasi likh di jaeygi. aur jab tum Namaz subh padho to isi tarah kaho, agar tum isi din faut ho gaey to tumharey liye us ( aag ( se khulaasi likh di jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2397,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh w Sham ye kalmaat zarur padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se duniya w aakhirat mein aafiyat ki darkhast karta hun, aey Allah ! main tujh se apney Deen , apni duniya aur apney ehle w ayaal aur maal mein maafi aur aafiyat ki darkhast karta hun, aey Allah! meri pardey wali baaton par parda dal aur merey khof w har usko aman mein badal dey, aey Allah! to merey samney sey, merey peechey sey, merey daain sey, merey baaeyn se aur merey ooper se meri hifazat farma, aur main is baat se ke main na-gahaan apney nichey se halak kya jaaun, teri panah chahta hun.'' ( Wakee ne kaha ( yani zamin mein dhansaaya jaaun. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2398,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye dua padhta hai : ''aey Allah ! ham ne subh ki, ham tujhey, terey arsh ko uthaney waley farishton, terey baqi farishton aur teri tamam makhluq ko gawah bana kar kehtey hain ke to Allah hai, terey siwa koi mabud nahin, to yakta hai, tera koi shareek nahin, aur be-shak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) terey bandey aur terey Rasool hain.'' to us roz us se jo gunah sarzad hoga to Allah usey maaf farma dega, aur agar wo ye kalmaat Sham ke waqt padhega to us raat us se jo gunah sarzad hoga, Allah usey maaf farma dega .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
2399,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman aadmi subh w Sham teen martaba kehta hai : ''main Allah ke rab honey par , Islam ke Deen honey par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Nabi honey par razi hun.'' to phir Allah par haq hai ke wo roze-qiyamat us ( shakhs ( ko razi karey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi."
2400,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab soney ka irada farmatey to aap apney sar ke nichey haath rakh kar ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! jis roz to apney bandon ko jama karey ya to apney bandon ko (qabron sey) uthaey to mujhey apney azab se bachaana.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
2401,aur Imam Ahmed (Raziallahu anhu) ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se usey riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed.
2402,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab soney ka irada farmatey to aap apna daayan haath apney rukhsar ke nichey rakhtey aur teen baar ye dua farmatey : ''aey Allah! to jis roz apney bandon ko uthaeyga us roz mujhey apney azab se bachaana.'' rawahu Abu-Dawud."
2403,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) let-tey waqt ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah! main terey izzat waley chehrey aur terey kamil kalmaat ke zariey her us chiz ke shar sey, jiski peshani to ne thaam rakhi hai, panah chahta hun, aey Allah! tu hi qarz aur gunah door karney wala hai, aey Allah! terey lashkar ko shikast nahin di ja sakti, tera wada khilaf nahin hota, kisi tawangar shakhs ki tawangari terey haan kaam nahin aa sakti, tu hi apni hamd ke sath paak hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2404,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney bistar par aaye aur teen martaba ye dua padhey : main Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo zinda, qaaim rakhney wala hai aur main usi ke huzur tauba karta hun.'' to Allah uskey gunah maaf kar deta hai chahey wo samandar ke jhaag ke barabar hon ya wadi Aalij ki ret ke zarrat ki tadaad ya darakhton ke patton ya duniya ke dinon ke barabar hon.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2405,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman let-tey waqt Quran Majeed ki koi sura tilawat karta hai to Allah is par eik farishta maamoor farma deta hai to phir uskey bedaar honey tak koi muzi (nuqsan pahunchaneywali) chiz uskey qarib nahin jati .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
2406,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do khaslatein aisi hain ke jo koi musalman unki hifazat karta hai wo jannat mein dakhil hoga, sun lo ! wo bahut aasan hain. lekin unhen baja laney waley qaleel hain, her Namaz ke baad das martaba Subhanallah kehna , das martaba Alhamdulillah kehna aur das martaba Allahu-akbar kehna.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney haath se unki gireh laga rahey they, farmaya : ''ye (paanchon namazon mein) zaban par eik sau pachas hain jabkey meezaan (taraazu) mein pandarah sau hain. aur jab wo let'tey waqt Subhanallah , Allahu-Akbar aur Alhamdulillah ki sau martaba ginti karey to ye zaban par sau hai jabkey tarazu mein hazar , tum mein se rozaana dhaai hazar guna kon karta hai?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, ham in (do khaslaton) ki kaisey hifazat nahin karengey? farmaya : ''tum mein se koi Namaz mein hota hai. shetan uskey paas aata hai to kehta hai : falan chiz yad karo, falan chiz yad karo yahan tak ke wo shakhs Namaz se farigh ho jata hai, shayad ke wo aisey na kar sakey aur wo uskey letney ke waqt bhi uskey paas aata hai aur wo usey sulaata rehta hai yahan tak ke wo so jata hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai . aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''do khaslatein aisi hain jin ki musalman banda hifazat nahin karta.'' aur isi tarah uski riwayat mein hai : ''meezaan  mein pandarah sau hai.'' kehney ke baad farmaya : jab wo apney bistar par aaye to wo chauntees martaba Allahu-akbar kehta hai, tentis martaba Alhamdulillah kehta hai aur tentis martaba Subhanallah kehta hai.'' aur Masaabeh ke aksar nuskhon mein Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2407,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ghannaam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subah ke waqt ye dua karta hai : ''aey Allah ! jo nemat mujhey ya teri makhluq mein se kisi ko mili hai wo sirf tujh akeley hi ki taraf se mili hai, tera koi shareek nahin, her qism ki tareef aur shukr terey hi liye hai.'' wo shakhs us roz ka shukr ada kar deta hai, aur jo shakhs Sham ke waqt yehi dua karta hai to wo us Sham ka shukr ada kar deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2408,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke jab aap apney bistar par tashrif latey to aap ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! zamin aur aasman ke rab ! aur her chiz ke rab ! daney aur guthli ko phadney waley ! Tauraat, Injeel aur Quran nazil karney waley ! main her shar wali chiz ke shar se jiski to peshani pakdey huey hai panah chahta hun, tu hi awwal hai tujh se pehley koi chiz nahin, tu hi aakhir hai terey baad koi chiz nahin, tu hi ghalib hai terey ooper koi chiz nahin, tu hi baatin hai aur tujh se koi chiz poshida nahin, mujh se qarz door kar dey , aur mujhey faqr (ghareebi) se ghani kar dey.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Muslim ne thodey se ikhtilaf ke sath riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Muslim."
2409,"Hazrat Abu-Zohraa Numaari (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney bistar par let jatey to ye dua padhtey they : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , maine apna pehlu Allah ke liye (bistar par) lagaya , aey Allah merey gunah maaf kar dey , merey shetan ko zaleel kar dey , mujhey tamam huquq se azad kar dey aur mujhey majlise-aa'laa mein shamil farma.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2410,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney bistar par tashrif latey to ye dua padhtey : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey kifaayat kiya, mujhey maskan (ghar) ata kiya, mujhey khilaya pilaya , jisney mujh par anginat inaam aur ehsan kiya, jisney mujhey ata farmaya to bahut ata farmaya , her haal mein Allah ka shukr hai, aey Allah ! her chiz ke rab aur uskey Malik aur badshah aur her chiz ke mabud main jahannam se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2411,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat kartey huey arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main be khuwaahi ki wajeh se puri raat nahin sota, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum apney bistar par aao to ye dua padho : ''aey Allah ! saton aasmano aur jin chizon par unhoney saya kiya hai unke rab ! zaminon aur jin chizon ko unhoney utha rakha hai unke rab ! shayatin aur jin ko unhoney gumrah kiya hai unke rab ! apni sari makhluq ke shar sey, ye ke un mein se koi mujh par ziyadti karey, mujhey panah deney wala ho ja , tujh se panah leney wala ghalib aata hai, teri sanaa aur taareef bahut ziyada hai aur terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya is riwayat ki asnaad qawi nahin. Hakam bin Zuher raawi ki ahadis ko baaz muhaddeseen ne tarak kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2412,"Hazrat Abu-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi subah karey to ye dua karey : ''ham ne aur tamam jahano ke parwardigar ke mulk ne subah ki, aey Allah ! main tujh se is din ki Fateh aur nusrat , iski roshni aur barkat aur iski hidayat ka sawal karta hun, aur is din ke aur iskey baad waley dino ke shar se teri panah chahta hun.'' phir jab Sham karey to bhi isi tarah dua padhey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2413,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakra bayan kartey hain, maine apney walid se kaha : abba jaan ! main aap ko her roz ye dua padhtey huey sunta hun : ''aey Allah ! mujhey merey badan mein aafiyat dey , aey Allah ! mujhey merey kanon mein aafiyat dey , aey Allah ! mujhey meri aakhon mein aafiyat dey , terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' aap subah aur Sham teen teen martaba inhen padhtey hain. to unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko in kalimaat ke zariey dua kartey huey suna hai lihaza mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ki iqtida (pairvi) karna chahta hun. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2414,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah kartey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''ham ne aur Allah ke mulk ne subah ki, her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai, kibriyaai (badaaee) aur azmat Allah ke liye hai, khalq aur Amr, lail aur nahar aur jo chizen in mein hain Allah ke liye hain, aey Allah ! is din ke awwal hissey ko salaah bana dey, iskey osat ko najaah aur aakhir ko falah (kaamiyabi) bana dey, aey sab se ziyada rehem karney waley.'' Imam Nauwi ne ibne Sunni ki riwayat se usey kitabe-azkaar mein riwayat kiya hai."
2415,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab subah kartey to ye dua kiya kartey they : ''ham ne fitrate Islam , kalma ikhlas , apney Nabi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Deen aur apney baap Ibrahim jo ke yaksoo they, mushrekin mein se nahin they, ki millat par subah ki.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Darmi."
2416,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs apni ehliya (biwi) se taaiuq qaaim karney se pahley ye dua padh ley : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , aey Allah ! hamen aur jo (aulad) to hamein ata farmaai usey shetan se bacha.'' to agar us waqt unke liye bachcha muqaddar kar diya gaya to shetan usey kabhi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakta.'' muttafaq aleh."
2417,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) karb (bechaini) aur takleef ke waqt ye dua padha kartey they : ''Allah Azeem aur Haleem ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur arshe azeem ke rab ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aasmano ke , zamin ke aur arshe karim ke rab ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
2418,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Surad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein gaali galoch karney lagey jabkey ham aap ke paas bethey huey they. aur un mein se eik sakht ghussay ki haalat mein doosrey ko gaali dey raha tha aur uska chehra surkh ho chuka tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main eik aisa kalima janta hun agar wo us kalime ko padh ley to uska ghussa khatam ho jaeyga, wo kalima ye hai : main shetan mardud se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aadmi se kaha : kya tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat nahin sun rahey? usney kaha : main deewana nahin hun ! muttafaq aleh."
2419,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum murgh ki aawaz suno to Allah se uska Fazal talab karo kyonkey usney farishta dekha hai, aur jab tum gadhey ki aawaz suno to shetan mardud se Allah ki panah talab karo kyonkey usney shetan dekha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2420,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar par rawana honey ke liye apney oont par Sawar ho jatey to aap teen baar Allahu-Akbar kehtey phir ye dua padhtey : ''paak hai wo zaat jisney hamarey liye isey musakhkhar kar diya jabkey ham is par taqat aur qudrat nahin rakhtey they. aey Allah ! ham is safar mein tujh se neki aur taqwa aur aisey amal ka sawal kartey hain jisey to pasand farmaai , aey Allah ! ye safar ham par aasan kar dey aur iski doori (lambi masafat ko hamarey liye) lapet (kar qarib) dey , aey Allah ! is safar main tu hi hamara sathi hai aur ghar mein naaib hai, aey Allah ! main safar ki shiddat aur mashaqqat , takleef-deh manzar aur ehale aur maal mein buri wapsi se teri panah chahta hun.'' aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis aatey to yehi dua padhtey aur iskey sath ye izafa farmatey : ''wapis lautney waley hain, tauba karney waley hain, ibadat karney waley hain, apney rab ki hamd karney waley hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
2421,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar kartey to aap safar ki shiddat aur mashaqqat , buri wapsi , nafe ke baad nuqsan , mazloom ki badduaa aur ehle aur maal mein burey manzar se panah talab kiya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
2422,"Hazrat Khaula binte Haakim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs kisi jagah padaaw daley aur ye dua padhey : ''maine Allah ke kamil kalmaat ke zariey , her us chiz ke shar se jo usney paida ki panah chahta hun.'' to jab tak wo us jagah qiyam pazeer rehta hai koi chiz usey nuqsan nahin pahunchati.'' rawahu Muslim."
2423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! guzishta raat bichchho ke kaatney se mujhey bahut takleef hui, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! agar tum ne Sham ke waqt yun kaha hota : ''main Allah ke kamil kalimaat ke zariey, us chiz ke shar sey, jo usney paida farmaai , panah chahta hun to wo tumhen nuqsan na pahunchata.'' rawahu Muslim."
2424,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar mein hotey aur sehri ka waqt hota to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''sun-ney waley ne sun liya ke ham ne Allah ki hamd bayan ki, uski nematen ham par achchhi hain, hamarey rab ! hamari iaa'nat farma , aur ham par mazeed ehsanaat farma , ham jahannam se Allah ki panah chahtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
2425,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghazwe ya Haj ya Umre se wapis tashrif latey to aap her buland jagah par teen martaba Allahu-Akbar kehtey, phir farmatey : Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat hai aur usi ke liye hamd hai aur wo her chiz par qadir hai, wapis lotney waley, tauba karney waley, ibadat karney waley, sajda karney waley, apney rab ki hamd bayan karney waley hain, Allah ne apna wada sach kar dikhaya . apney bandey ki nusrat farmaee aur us akeley ne lashkaron ko shikast di.'' muttafaq aleh."
2426,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae ehzaab ke moqe par mushrekin ke khilaf dua ki to arz kiya : ''aey Allah ! kitab utaarney waley, jald hisab leney waley, aey Allah ! lashkaron ko shikast dey , aey Allah ! unhen khub shikast dey aur unhen hila kar rakh dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2427,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Busr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey walid ke paas tashrif laye to ham ne khana aur khajoor , ghi aur paneer se tayyar karda halwa aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to aapney us se khaya (khaaya), phir khajuren pesh ki gaeen to aap unhen khatey aur guthliyaan apni do ungliyon ke darmiyan phainktey jatey, aap angusht shahadat aur darmiyani ungli ikhatti kartey they, aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap guthliyaan apni dono ungliyon , angusht shahadat aur darmiyani ungli ki pusht par phenk rahey they, phir pani pesh kiya gaya to aapney usey nosh farmaya , phir merey walid ne aap ki sawari ki lagaam pakadtey huey arz kiya : hamarey liye Allah se dua farmaeyn, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! to ne jo kuchh inhen ata kiya hai is mein barkat farma, inki maghfirat farma aur in par rehem farma.'' rawahu Muslim."
2428,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab chaand dekhtey to aap ye dua padhtey they : ''aey Allah ! to isey aman aur eman aur salamti aur Islam ke sath ham par tulu farma , (aey chaand !) mera aur tera rab Allah hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2429,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi musibat-zada shakhs ko dekh kar ye dua padhta hai : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey is chiz se aafiyat di jis mein tujhey mubtala kiya hai, aur usney mujhey apni bahut si makhluq par bahut ziyada fazilat di.'' to usey wo musibat aur bimari nahin pahuncheygi chahey (chaahe) wo koi bhi ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2430,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se isey riwayat kiya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Amr bin Dinar raawi qawi nahin. rawahu ibne-Maja."
2431,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs baazar mein dakhil hotey waqt ye dua padhta hai : Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ke liye badshahat aur hamd hai, wohi zinda karta hai aur maarta hai, wo zinda hai kabhi mareyga nahin, her qism ki khair aur bhalai usi ke haath mein hai, aur wo her chiz par qadir hai.'' to Allah uskey liye das lakh nekiyan likh leta hai, uski das lakh khataeyn maaf kar deta hai, uskey das lakh darjaat buland kar deta hai aur uskey liye jannat main eik ghar bana deta hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur Sharahus-sunnah mein ''jo shakhs baazar mein jaey'' ke alfaz ke bajaey ''jisney kisi badey tijaarati markaz mein ye dua padhi.'' ke alfaz hain. rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Sharahus-sunnah."
2432,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko in alfaz ke sath dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se itmaam (khaatmae) nemat ka sawal karta hun.'' to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon si chiz itmaam (khaatmae) nemat hai? '' usney kaha : dua jiskey zariey mein khair (ziyada-maal) ki ummid karta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' itmaam (khaatmae) nemat to jannat mein dakhila aur jahannam se khulaasi hai.'' aur aapney kisi doosrey aadmi ko dua kartey huey suna : ''aey jalal aur ikram waley !'' to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari dua qubul ho gaee , ab sawal karo.'' isi tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sabr ka sawal karta hun.'' to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne Allah se musibat maangi hai, us se aafiyat ka sawal karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2433,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi majlis mein bethey aur uski be-maqsad aur be-hooda baaten ziyada ho jaeyn aur phir wo uthney se pehley ye dua : ''aey Allah ! to apni hamd ke sath paak hai, main gawahi deta hun ke terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, mein tujh se maghfirat talab karta hun aur terey huzur tauba karta hun.'' padhta hai to uski us majlis mein honey wali khataeyn maaf kar di jati hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Al-Behaqi."
2434,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unki sawari ke liye eik janwer laya gaya, jab unhoney rikaab mein paaon rakha to kaha : ''بسم اللہ'' jab uski pusht par biraajmaan ho gaey to kaha : ''Alhamdulillah'' phir farmaya : ''paak hai wo zaat jisney isey hamarey tabey kar diya jabkey ham to iski qudrat nahin rakhtey they, aur be-shak ham apney rab ki taraf palat kar janey waley hain.'' phir unhoney teen martaba ''Alhamdulillah'' teen martaba ''Allah akbar'' kaha , phir kaha : ''paak hai tu, maine hi apni jaan par zulm kiya, isliye mujhey bakhsh dey , kyonkey terey siwa koi gunah nahin bakhshta.'' phir wo muskuraaey, un se puchha gaya, Ameerul-momeneen ! aap kis chiz se muskuraaey hain? unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is tarah kartey huey dekha jis tarah maine kiya, phir aap muskuraaey to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap kis chiz se muskuraaey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tera rab apney us bandey se bahut khush hota hai jab wo kehta hai : ''merey rab ! merey gunah maaf kar dey.'' rab taala farmata hai : ''wo janta hai ke merey siwa koi aur gunah maaf nahin karta.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2435,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi shakhs ko alwidaa kartey to aap uska haath thaamey rakhtey yahan tak ke wo aadmi khud Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath chhod deta , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua padhtey : ''main tumharey Deen , tumhari amanat aur tumharey aakhiri amal ko Allah ke supurd karta hun.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''terey amalon ke khaatmey ko.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , aur in dono (Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja) ki riwayat mein (وَآخِرَ عَمَلِکَ) ka zikr nahin kiya gaya. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2436,"Hazrat Abdullah Khitmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lashkar rawana karney ka irada farmatey to yun dua farmatey : ''main tumharey Deen , tumhari amanaton aur tumharey aakhiri aamaal ko Allah ke supurd karta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2437,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main safar ka irada rakhta hun, aap mujhey zaade-raah ata farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tumhen taqwe ka zaade-raah ata farmaey.'' usney arz kiya : kuchh ziyada farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo tumharey gunah bakhsh dey.'' usney arz kiya, merey waliden aap par qurban hon, ziyada farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jahan bhi ho Allah tumharey liye khair aur bhalai aasan farma dey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
2438,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke kisi aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main safar karna chahta hun, lihaza aap mujhey koi wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke taqwe aur her oonchi jagah par Allahu-Akbar padhney ka iltizaam (wajib) karna.'' jab wo aadmi wapis chala gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! uski doori aur masafat ko lapet (kar samet) dey aur safar ko uskey liye aasan kar dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2439,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar mein hotey aur raat ho jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''zameen ! mera aur tera rab Allah hai, main terey shar sey, jo kuchh tujh mein hai uskey shar sey, jo tujh mein paida kiya gaya hai uskey shar se aur jo chiz teri satah par chal rahi hai uskey shar se Allah ki panah chahta hun. main sher , kalay naag , sanp aur bichho ke shar se aur basti ke baasiyon aur shetan aur zurriyat (aulade shetan) ke shar se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2440,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jihad ke liye nikaltey to yun dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! tu hi mera bazu hai, tu hi mera madadgar hai, main teri hi tofiq se dushman ki chaalon ko radd karta hun, teri hi madad se (dushman par) hamla karta hun aur teri tofiq aur nusrat se qitaal karta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2441,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kisi qom se andesha hota to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yun dua farmatey they : ''aey Allah ham unke muqabley mein tujhey kartey hain, aur unki shararaton se teri panah mein aatey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
2442,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar se bahar tashrif ley jatey to dua farmatey : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , maine Allah par tawakkul kiya, aey Allah ! ham teri panah chahtey hain ke ham (siraate-mustaqeem (seedhey raaste) sey) phisal jaeyn ya gumrah ho jaeyn , ya ham zulm karen ya ham par zulm kiya jaey, ya ham kisi se jihalat se pesh ayen ya hamarey sath jihalat se pesh aaya jaey.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja ki riwayat mein hai, Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi merey ghar se tashrif ley jatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aasman ki taraf nazar utha kar dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun ke main gumrah ho jaaun ya gumrah kar diya jaaun , ya mein zulm karun ya mujh par zulm kiya jaey, ya mein jihalat se pesh aaun ya mujh se jihalat se pesh aaya jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2443,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi ghar se nikaltey waqt ye dua padhey : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , maine Allah par tawakkul kiya, gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz Allah ki tofiq se hai.'' to tab usey kaha jata hai : teri raahnumai kar di gaee , tujhey kifaayat kar di gaee aur to bacha liya gaya. shetan us se alag ho jata hai, aur doosra shetan kehta hai : tumhara aisey aadmi par kaisey zor chal sakta hai jiski raahnumai kar di gaee , usey kifaayat kar di gaee aur usey bacha liya gaya.'' Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne (لہ الشیطان) tak riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
2444,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apney ghar dakhil ho to ye dua padhey : ''aey Allah ! main dakhil honey ki jagah aur nikalney ki jagah ki bhalai ka tujh se sawal karta hun, Allah ke naam ke sath ham dakhil huey aur apney rab Allah par ham ne tawakkul kiya, phir wo apney ehle khana ko salam karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2445,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab shaadi ke moqe par kisi shakhs ko dua detey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''Allah terey liye barkat karey aur tum dono par barkat karey aur tum dono ko khair par ikhatta karey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2446,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs kisi aurat se shaadi karey ya koi ghulam khareedey to wo yun dua karey : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se uski khair aur bhalai aur is chiz ki khair aur bhalai ka jis par to ne isey paida kiya, sawal karta hun, aur main iskey shar se aur is chiz ke shar se jis par to ne isey paida kiya teri panah chahta hun.'' aur jab oont khareedey to uski kohan ki choti pakad kar yehi dua karey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein aurat aur khaadim ke barey mein hai : ''phir uski peshani ke baal pakad kar barkat ki dua karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2447,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghamgeen shakhs ki dua hai : ''aey Allah ! main teri rehmat ka umeedwar hun, mujhey lamha bhar ke liye bhi merey nafs ke supurd na karna , merey tamam halaat durust kar dey , terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2448,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi shakhs ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ghamon aur qarzon ne mujhey gher rakha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisa kaliam na bataaun ke jab tum wo kaliam padho to Allah tumharey gham door kar dey aur teri taraf se tera qarz ada kar dey?'' usney arz kiya : ji haan , kyon nahin ! zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : subh aur Sham ye dua padha karo : ''aey Allah ! main fikr aur gham se teri panah chahta hun, main susti aur kahili se teri panah chahta hun, main bukhl (kanjusi) aur buzdili se teri panah chahta hun, main qarz ke ziyada honey aur logon ke ghalbe se teri panah chahta hun.'' wo shakhs bayan karta hai : maine ye wazeefa kiya to Allah ne mera gham door kar diya aur mera qarz ada kar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2449,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik makatib unke paas aaya to usney kaha : main apni azadi ke liye tey-shuda raqam ada karney se aajiz hun lihaza aap (Raziallahu anhu) meri madad farmaeyn, unhoney farmaya : kya main tujhey chand kalimaat na sikhaaun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey sikhaey they, agar tujh par kisi badey pahad ke barabar qarz hoga to Allah usey tujh se ada kar dega, kaho : ''aey Allah ! to apni halal karda chiz ke zariey apni haram karda chiz se mujhey kafi ho ja aur apney Fazal ke zariey apney ilawa mujhey sab se be-niyaz kar dey.'' ham Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ( اِذَا سَمِعْتُمْ نُبَاحَ الْکِلَابِ ( baab (تغطیۃ الاوانی) mein Insha-Allah zikr karengey. rawahu Tirmizi aur al-Behaqi."
2450,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi majlis mein bethtey ya Namaz padhtey to aap chand kalimaat padhtey , maine un kalmaat ke barey mein aap se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to achchhi baaten ki gaeen to ye kalimaat roze-qiyamat tak un par bator mehar hongey, aur agar koi buri baaten ki gaeen to ye kalimaat unke liye kaffara hongey : ''aey Allah ! to apni hamd ke sath paak hai, terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, main tujh se maghfirat talab karta hun aur terey huzur tauba karta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2451,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, unhen ye khabar pahunchi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaand dekhtey to teen baar farmatey : ''khair aur bhalai ke chaand ! main us zaat par eman laya jisney mujhey paida farmaya.'' phir farmatey : ''her qism ki tareef us zaat ke liye hai jo falan mahiney ko ley gaya aur falan mahina ley aaya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2452,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bahut ziyada gham ka shikar ho to wo ye dua karey : ''aey Allah ! main tera banda hun, terey bandey aur teri londi ka beta hun, main terey qabze aur qudrat ke tehat hun, meri peshani terey haath mein hai, tera hukm merey barey mein nafiz honey wala hai, tera merey mutalliq faisla adl par mabni hai, main terey her us naam sey, jo to ne apney liye rakha , ya to ne usey apni kitab mein nazil kiya, ya to ne apni makhluq mein se kisi ko sikhaya , ya to ne apney bandon ko ilhaam kiya, ya to ne apney paas ghaib ke khazaney mein usey makhsus kar liya , tujh se sawal karta hun ke to Quran ko merey dil ki bahaar, merey fikr aur gham ka ilaj bana dey.'' jo shakhs ye kalimaat padhta hai to Allah uskey gham door kar deta hai aur huzn aur gham ko farhat aur musarrat (khushi) mein tabdeel kar deta hai. rawahu Rizeen."
2453,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham ooper chadhtey to Allahu-Akbar kehtey aur jab nichey utartey to Subhanallah kehtey they. Bukhari."
2454,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko koi takleef pahunchti to aap ye dua kiya kartey they : ''aey zinda qaaim rehney waley ! main teri rehmat ke zariey madad talab karta hun.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur mehfooz nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
2455,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwe-khandaq ke moqe par ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya koi kalima hai jo ham padhein ab to kalejey munh ko aa rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan : aey Allah ! hamare pardey ki chizon par parda dal dey aur hamarey khof ko aman ata farma.'' Allah ne aandhi ke zariey aap ke dushman ka rukh badal diya, Allah ne aandhi ke zariey shikast di.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2456,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baazar tashrif ley jatey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , aey Allah ! main, is baazar aur jo is mein hai uski khair aur bhalai ka tujh se sawal karta hun aur iskey aur ismein mojud shar se teri panah chahta hun, aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun ke main is mein koi ghatey ka soda karun.'' rawahu al-Behaqi."
2457,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aazmaesh ki shiddat , bad-bakhti ki aamad , taqdir ki zahmat aur dushmanon ki khushi se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2458,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main fikr aur gham , aajizi aur susti , buzdili aur bukhl, qarzey ke bojh aur logon ke ghalbey se teri panah chahta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
2459,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main susti , budhapey , tawaan (jurmaane) aur gunah se teri panah chahta hun, aey Allah ! main aag ke azab , aag ke fitne , qabr ke fitney , qabr ke azab , tawangari ke fitne ke shar sey, faqr ke fitne ke shar se aur Masih dajjaal ke fitne ke shar se teri panah chahta hun, aey Allah ! merey gunahon ko barf aur olon ke pani se dho dey , merey dil ko aisey saaf kar dey jis tarah safed kapdey ko mail se saaf kiya jata hai, aur merey darmiyan aur merey gunahon ke darmiyan aisi doori paida farma dey jaisey to ne mashriq aur maghrib ke darmiyan doorii paida farmaee.'' muttafaq aleh."
2460,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main aajizi aur susti , buzdili aur bukhl, budhapey aur azabe-qabr se teri panah chahta hun, aey Allah ! merey nafs ko uska taqwa ata farma , uska tazkiya farma aur to behtareen tazkiya karney wala hai, to uska karsaz aur madadgar hai, aey Allah ! main aisey ilm se jo nafa mand na ho, aisey dil se jo darta na ho, aisey nafs se jo bharta na ho aur aisi dua se jo qubul na ho teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
2461,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main teri nemat ke zaayel (khatam) ho janey , teri aafiyat ke badal janey , terey azab ke nagahaani aa janey se aur teri tamam naraziyon se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
2462,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! maine jo amal kiya uskey shar se aur jo amal nahin kiya uskey shar se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
2463,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! maine teri itaat ikhtiyar ki, main tujh par eman laya , tujh par tawakkul kiya, teri taraf ruju kiya, teri tofiq se (dushmanon ke sath) jhagda kiya, aey Allah ! main teri izzat aur ghalbe ki panah chahta hun ke to mujhey gumrah kar dey , terey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to zinda hai jisey maut nahin aaeygi jabkey jin aur insan faut ho jaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2464,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main chaar chizon se teri panah chahta hun, aisey ilm se jo nafa mand na ho, aisey dil se jo darta na ho, aisey nafs se jo bharta na ho aur aisi dua se jo qubul na ho.'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2465,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai.
2466,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paanch chizon se panah talab kiya kartey they : buzdili aur bukhl sey, umr ki kharabi sey, seene ke fitney (yani waswasey) se aur azabe-qabr se. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2467,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main faqr (gharibi) aur qillat aur zillat se teri panah chahta hun, aur main teri panah chahta hun ke main zulm karun ya mujh par zulm kiya jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2468,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main tanaaza' (jhagdey) aur ikhtilaf , nifaq aur burey akhlaq se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2469,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main bhook se teri panah chahta hun, kyonkey wo bura sathi hai, aur main khayanat se teri panah chahta hun kyonkey wo buri khaslat hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2470,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main baras aur juzaam (phulbhari aur kodh ki bimari) , jinnon aur buri bimariyon se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2471,"Hazrat Qutbaa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main burey akhlaq , burey aamaal aur buri khaahishat se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2472,"Hazrat Shutair bin Shakal bin Humaid apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey koi aisa dam sikhaein ke main uskey zariey panah hasil kiya karun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : kaho : ''aey Allah ! main apney kaan , apni aankh , apni zaban , apney dil aur apni mani ki burai se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur Nasai."
2473,"Hazrat Abu Yusr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun ke koi imarat mujh par gir padey , main kisi oonchi jagah se girney , doob janey , jal janey aur budhapey se teri panah chahta hun, aur main teri panah chahta hun ke maut ke waqt shetan mujhey bad-hawaas bana dey , aur main teri panah chahta hun ke main teri raah mein peeth pher kar bhagtey huey faut hun, aur main teri panah chahta hun ke kisi chiz ke dasney se meri maut waqey ho.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai , aur unhoney dusri riwayat mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''aur gham se.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
2474,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se aisi tamaa (lalach) (laalach) se panah talab karo jo gunah ki taraf ley jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Al-Behaqi."
2475,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaand ki taraf dekha to farmaya : ''Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ! iskey shar se Allah ki panah talab karo, kyonkey yehi wo ghaasiq hai jab be Noor ho jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2476,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey walid se farmaya : ''Husain ! aaj tum kitney mabudon ki puja kartey ho? ''merey walid ne kaha : saat ki, chhe zamin par hain aur eik aasman mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney nafe aur nuqsan ke liye kisey khas kartey ho?'' usney kaha : jo aasmano mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Husain ! sun lo ! agar tum Islam qubul kar lo to main tumhen do kalimey sikhaaun ga jo tumhen faeyda pahunchaaeyngey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, jab Husain musalman ho gaey to unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey wo do kalimey sikhaein jin ka aapney mujh se wada kiya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : kaho : ''aey Allah ! meri bhalai mujhey ilhaam farma dey , aur mujhey merey nafs ki kharabi se bacha ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2477,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs neend mein ghabra jaey to wo yun kahe : ''main Allah ke kamil kalmaat ke zariey , uskey ghazab , uskey azaab, uskey bandon ke shar aur shayatin ke waswason se ke wo merey paas ayen, panah chahta hun, wo (waswasey) usey hergiz nuqsan nahin pahunchaaeyngey.'' Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) apney baligh bachchon ko ye kalimaat sikhaya kartey they, aur jo abhi baligh nahin huey they to aap unhen kaghaz par likh kar unke galey mein dal diya kartey they. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi . aur ye alfaz Tirmizi ke hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
2478,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs teen martaba Allah se jannat ka sawal karta hai to jannat kehti hai : aey Allah ! isey jannat mein dakhil farma , aur jo shakhs teen martaba jahannam se panah talab karta hai to jahannam arz karti hai : aey Allah ! isey jahannam se bacha.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
2479,"Hazrat Qaaqaa bayan kartey hain, Kab Ahbaar ne kaha : agar main chand kalimaat na kahun to Yahudi (jadu ke zariey) mujhey gadhaa bana de , un se puchha gaya, wo kalimaat kon se hain? unhoney kaha : main Allah azeem ke chehrey ke zariey panah hasil karta hun jis se badh kar koi chiz nahin, aur Allah ke kamil kalimaat ke zariey (panah hasil karta hun) jin se koi nek aage nikal sakta hai na koi faajir, aur Allah ke asmaye-husna ke zariey jinhen main janta hun aur jinhen main nahin janta , her chiz ke shar se panah chahta hun jo usney paida farmaai aur phelai aur munasib banai. rawahu Malik."
2480,"Hazrat Muslim bin Abi Bakra bayan kartey hain, merey walid Namaz ke baad dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main kufr aur faqr (ghareebi) aur azabe-qabr se teri panah chahta hun.'' main bhi inhen padha karta tha, unhoney kaha : beta tum ne inhen kis se seekha hai? maine arz kiya, aap sey, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) inhen Namaz ke baad kaha kartey they. Tirmizi, Nasai. albatta Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne ''Namaz ke baad, ka zikr nahin kiya. aur Imam Ahmed (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadees ke alfaz riwayat kiye aur unki riwayat mein hai, her Namaz ke baad.'' rawahu Nasai, Tirmizi aur Ahmed."
2481,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! main kufr aur qarz se teri panah chahta hun.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya kufr , qarz ke barabar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan !'' aur dusri riwayat mein hai : ''aey Allah ! main kufr aur faqr (ghareebi) se teri panah chahta hun.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kiya : wo dono barabar hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan !'' rawahu Nasai."
2482,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap ye dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! meri khataeyn , meri jihalat , aur tamam umur (baton) mein jo mujh se ziyadti hui jisey to mujh se ziyada janta hai, maaf farma dey , aey Allah ! maine jo daanista kiya jo bhool chook se hua aur jo kuchh amadan kiya ye sab kuchh mujh mein hai to usey maaf kar dey , aey Allah ! maine jo aagey bheja aur jo peechhey chhoda , maine jo elania kiya aur jo chhup kar kiya aur jisey to mujh se ziyada janta hai sab maaf kar dey, tu hi aagey karney wala aur tu hi peechhey karney wala hai aur to her chiz par qadir hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2483,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! merey Deen ki islah farma jo ke merey tamam maamlat ka muhafiz hai, meri duniya ki islah farma jis mein mera muaash hai, meri aakhirat ki islah farma jahan mujhey lot kar jana hai, zindagi ko her qism ki khair aur bhalai mein izafe ka baais bana aur maut ko her qism ke shar se rahat ka baais bana.'' rawahu Muslim."
2484,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se hidayat , taqwe aur iffat aur tawangari ka sawal karta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
2485,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kaho , aey Allah ! meri raahnumai farma , mujhey durust rakh aur (aey Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) raahnumai se raah hidayat pe chalney ka tasawwur aur durust honey se teer ka sa durust hona tasawwur mein rakh. rawahu Muslim."
2486,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ashjai apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : eik aadmi tha jab usney Islam qubul kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Namaz sikhai , phir usey in kalimaat ke zariey dua karney ka hukm farmaya : ''aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey , mujh par rehem farma , mujhey aafiyat mein rakh aur mujhey rizq ata farma.'' rawahu Muslim."
2487,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aksar ye dua hua karti thi ''aey Allah ! hamein duniya mein bhalai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhalai ata farma, aur hamein aag ke azab se bacha.'' muttafaq aleh."
2488,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : ''aey merey rab ! meri madad farma aur merey khilaf (merey dushmanon ki) madad na farma, meri nusrat farma aur merey khilaf nusrat na farma, merey liye tadbeer farma aur merey khilaf tadbeer na farma, mujhey hidayat nasib farma aur merey liye hidayat aasan farma dey, jo shakhs mujh par zulm aur sarkashi karey uskey khilaf meri nusrat farma , aey merey rab ! mujhey apna shukr guzar , tera zikr karney wala, tujh se darney wala, tera intehai itaat guzar , teri aajizi ikhtiyar karney wala aur teri taraf bahut ziyada jhukne wala, ruju karney wala bana , aey merey rab ! meri tauba qubul farma , merey gunah maaf farma , meri dua qubul farma , meri hujjat aur daleel Sabit farma , meri zaban ko durust farma , merey dil ki raahnumai farma , aur merey seeney ka keena door farma.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2489,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey huey phir roney lagey aur farmaya : ''Allah se maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal karo, kyonkey kisi ko eman ki dolat nasib ho janey ke baad aafiyat se behtar koi chiz ata nahin ki gaee.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai aur aur iski sanad gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2490,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kon si dua afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney rab se duniya aur aakhirat mein aafiyat aur muaafaat (baham (aapas mein) darguzar karna) maango , phir wo doosrey roz hazir hua to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kon si dua afzal hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isi tarah farmaya , phir teesrey roz aap ke paas aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey phir wesay hi farmaya , aur farmaya : ''jab tujhey duniya aur aakhirat mein aafiyat aur muaafaat mil gaee to to kamiyab ho gaya .'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai aur iski sanad gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2491,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazid Khitmi (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap apni dua mein kaha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! mujhey apni aur us chiz ki mohabbat ata farma jiski mohabbat mujhey terey yahaan faeyda pahunchaey , aey Allah to jo meri pasandida chiz mujhey ata farmaai to usey merey liye aisi chiz ki taqwiyat ka baais bana jisey to pasand karta hai, aey Allah ! to meri jis pasandida chiz ko mujh se rok ley to usko merey us kaam ke liye baaise faraaghat bana jisey to pasand karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2492,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aksar oqaat kisi majlis se uthney se pehley in kalimaat ke zariey apney Sahaba ke liye dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! hamein apne dar se aisa hissey ata farma jo hamarey aur teri muaasi aur nafarmani ke darmiyan haael (rukawat) ho jaey, aur apni itaat se aisa hissey ata farma jiskey zariey to hamein apni jannat mein pahuncha dey , aur yaqin se aisa hissey nasib farma jo duniya ke masaayib (musibaten) ham par aasan kar dey , jab tak to hamein zinda rakhey, hamarey kanon , hamari aakhon aur hamari quwat se bahra mand farma , aur in (mazkura chizon) ko baqi rakhna, jo shakhs ham par zulm karey is par hamara ghazab nazil farma, hamarey Deen (mein kami) ke barey mein ham par koi musibat nazil na farma, duniya ko hamara sab se bada maqsad bana na hamarey ilm ka maqsad aur khaahish bana , aur ham par kisi aisey ko musallat na farma jo ham par rehem na karey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2493,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kiya kartey they : aey Allah ! to ne mujhey jo ilm ata kiya us se mujhey faeyda pahuncha , aur mujhey aisa ilm ata farma jo mujhey faeyda pahunchaey aur merey ilm mein izafa farma , her haal mein Allah ka shukr hai aur main jahannamiyon ke haal se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sanad se gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2494,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ''wahi'' nazil hoti to aap ke chehrey ke paas shehad ki makkhiyon ki si bhin-bhinahat sunai deti thi, eik roz aap par ""wahi"" nazil hui to ham ne thodi der intizar kiya, aap se wo kaifiyat jati rahi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qibla rukh ho kar haath uthaey aur yun dua ki : ''aey Allah ! hamein ziyada kar , kam na kar , hamein izzat ata karna , zaleel na karna , hamein ata karna , mehroom na rakhna , hamein tarjeeh dena aur hamarey khilaf kisi ko tarjeeh na dena , hamein razi kar aur ham se razi ho ja.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujh par das aayaate nazil hui hain, jo unki hifazat aur khayal kerega jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' phir aapney (قَدْ اَفْلَحَ الْمُوْمِنُوْنَ) se das aayaate-tilawat farmaai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
2495,"Hazrat Usman bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik na-bina shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, Allah se dua karen ke wo mujhey aafiyat ata farmaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar tum chaho to main dua karta hun aur agar tum chaho to sabr karo to wo tumharey liye behtar hai.'' usney arz kiya, aap Allah se dua farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm farmaya ke khub achchhi tarah wuzu karey aur in alfaz ke sath dua karey : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun aur terey nabi, Nabi rehmat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zariey teri taraf mutawajjeh hota hun, be-shak maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zariey apney rab ki taraf tawajjoh ki taake meri is hajat ke barey mein merey haq mein faisla kiya jaey, aey Allah ! merey barey mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shafaat qubul farma.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2496,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki ye dua thi : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se teri mohabbat ka, us shakhs ki mohabbat ka jo tujh se mohabbat karta ho aur us amal ka sawal karta hun jo mujhey teri mohabbat tak pahuncha dey, aey Allah ! to apni mohabbat, mujhey meri jaan, merey ehle aur ayaal , maal aur thandey pani se ziyada mehbub bana dey.'' abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka zikr kartey to unke mutalliq bayan kartey huey farmatey : ''wo tamam insanon se ziyada ibadat guzar they.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2497,"Hazrat Ata bin Saaib apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Namaz padhaai to is mein ikhtisaar kiya to kuch logon ne unhen kaha : aapney Namaz mein kami aur ikhtisaar kiya hai? unhoney farmaya is se mujhey koi farq nahin pada , maine is mein kuchh duayen ki hain jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni thin, jab wo (janey ke liye) khadey huey to un logon mein se eik aadmi, wo merey walid hi they lekin unhoney apna naam chupaey rakha, unke peechhey peechhey gaya aur un se dua ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, phir wapis aa kar usey logon ko bataya : ''aey Allah ! apney ilme-ghaib aur makhluq par apni qudrat ke zariey us waqt tak zinda rakhna jab tak mera zinda rehna terey ilm ke mutabiq merey liye behtar ho. aur jab to samjhey ke mera faut hona merey liye behtar hai to mujhey faut kar dena , aey Allah ! main ghaib aur hazir mein tujh se kalimaae-haq ka sawal karta hun, main faqr (ghareebi) aur ghani mein tujh se beech ki zindagi ka sawal karta hun, main khatam na honey wali nematon ka tujh se sawal karta hun, main khatam na honey wali aakhon ki thandak ka tujh se sawal karta hun, main qaza ke baad raza ka tujh se sawal karta hun, main maut ke baad khushgawar zindagi ka tujh se sawal karta hun, main kisi shadeed takleef aur gumrahkun fitney ke baghair teri mulaqat ke shoq aur terey chehrey ko dekhney ki lazzat ka tujh se sawal karta hun, aey Allah ! zeenat-emaan se saji hui zindagi Ata farma aur hamein hidayat par Sabit rehney wala haadi bana.'' rawahu Nasai."
2498,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz ke baad ye dua kiya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se nafa bakhsh ilm , maqbool amal aur halal rizq ka sawal karta hun.'' rawahu Ahmed, ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi."
2499,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se eik dua yad ki jisey main chhodta nahin : ''aey Allah ! mujhey aisa bana dey ke main tera bahut ziyada shukr karun, tera bahut ziyada zikr karun, teri nasihat ki bahut ittiba karun aur terey ehkam ko bahut ziyada yad karun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2500,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kartey they : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sehat , iffat , amanat , Husne-akhlaq aur taqdir par razi rehney ka sawal karta hun.'' rawahu al-Behaqi."
2501,"Hazrat Umme-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! merey dil ko nifaq sey, merey amal ko riya sey, meri zaban ko jhoot se aur meri aakhon ko khayanat se paak kar dey, kyonkey to khayanat karney wali aakhon ko janta hai aur jo kuchh seeney (dil) chupatey hain to usey bhi janta hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein الدعوات الکبیر mein riwayat ki hain. rawahu al-Behaqi."
2502,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik musalman shakhs ki iyaadat ki, wo perindey ke bachchey ki tarah kamzor ho chuka tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (us ki ye haalat dekh kar) usey farmaya : ''kya tum Allah se koi dua ya kisi khas chiz ka sawal kartey ho?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan , main kaha karta tha : aey Allah ! to ne jo mujhey aakhirat mein saza deeni hai wo to mujhey duniya mein dey ley. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Subhanallah ! tum (duniya mein) uski taqat rakhtey ho na tum (aakhirat mein) uski istataat rakhtey ho, tum ne aisey kyon na kaha : aey Allah ! hamein duniya mein bhalai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhalai ata farma , aur hamein jahannam ke azab se bacha .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, us shakhs ne in kalimaat ke zariey dua ki to Allah ne usey shifa ata kar di. rawahu Muslim."
2503,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi momin ki shaan nahin ke wo apney aap ko zaleel karey.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : wo apney aap ko kaisey zaleel karta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey masaayib (musibaton) ko (dua ya aamaal ke zariey) dawat deta hai. jin ki wo taqat nahin rakhta.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. (rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi)."
2504,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dua sikhai to farmaya : kaho : ''aey Allah ! mera baatin, merey zahir se behtar kar dey aur merey zahir ko Saleh bana dey, aey Allah ! to ne jo logon ko ehal aur maal aur aulad dey rakhi hai mujhey us se Saleh ata farma, jo khud gumrah hon na gumrah karne wale.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
